NK084(yu)001:1: // zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba zhes bya ba bzhugs pa lags soha&a&a&a //
NK084(yu)001:6: dgos pa'i don la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:7: man ngag rtsom pa la bar chad kyi bgegs zhi bar bya ba'i dgos pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:8: ya rabs dam pa dang tshul bstun pa'i sgo nas dad pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i dgos pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:9: yi dam gyi lha mi spong ba'i dgos pa yod pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:10: bsdus pa'i don ni bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:13: tshul lam thabs ji ltar rtsal /
NK084(yu)001:14: rtsal ba la don ched ci yod do //
NK084(yu)001:15: de la yul gang zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:16: dpal kun tu bzang po rgyal ba drug pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:18: sngon 'byung du slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:19: rjes 'jug tu bshad pa po rnams so //
NK084(yu)001:21: lus gus pa dang ngag snyan pa dang bcas /
NK084(yu)001:22: sems dang ba dang bcas nas brtsal ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:24: don gyi phyag 'tshal bas rig pa nyid kun tu bzang por rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:26: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub kyi rgyur 'gyur ba'i don no //
NK084(yu)001:27: tshig gi don ni gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:28: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po ngos bzung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:29: de'i che ba la sku lnga lhun grub tu bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:30: dang po rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po ngos gzung ba la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:32: dgongs ye shes dang dkyil dpyod dang /
NK084(yu)001:34: gnyis pa de'i che ba ni lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:37: mngon par byang chub thugs pa'i sku dang /
NK084(yu)001:39: sprul pa'i sku dang dkyil 'khor lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:40: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag /de ma nor bzhin ma bcos /
NK084(yu)001:41: de'i ngang du gshegs pa ni gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:42: grol lam du gshegs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:44: grol lam ni rang 'byung ye shes sku nyams su gtar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:45: thabs lam du gshegs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:46: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes sku nyams su gtar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:47: kun gyi ni de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad spyir bsdus pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:48: bdag ni chos nyid ye nas ma bcos ma slad
NK084(yu)001:49: pa'i don ji lta bar rang gis mngon gsum du
NK084(yu)001:50: byas pa ni / dpal kun tu bzang po phyogs
NK084(yu)001:51: bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK084(yu)001:52: byas pa ni / bdag nyid / rgyal ba drug pa de /
NK084(yu)001:53: dngos su mnyam pa nyid kyi chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:54: ye shes rgya mtsho' rab zab thugs //
NK084(yu)001:56: grol lam rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po dang /
NK084(yu)001:57: thabs lam lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:59: rtogs pas na ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:60: de'i dpe' ni rgya mtsho' ste /
NK084(yu)001:61: gting dpag par dka' bas zab pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:62: de dang kun bzang gi thugs 'dra bas na thugs so //
NK084(yu)001:63: de bas na de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rang byung gi ye shes ni /
NK084(yu)001:65: gdul byas dpag par dka' ba ni dpe' rgya mtsho'i lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:66: de ni longs spyod rdzogs skur 'byung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:68: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes de las ma g.yos
NK084(yu)001:69: par zhi ba dang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK084(yu)001:70: ma lus ma rtsal bar gdul bya yi snang ba
NK084(yu)001:72: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i
NK084(yu)001:73: gter dang 'dra'o de yang zad mi shes shing 'dod
NK084(yu)001:74: dgur 'byung ba ni sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK084(yu)001:75: rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal te //
NK084(yu)001:76: chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa yin pas thams cad du snang ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:77: ma rtsal ba'i phyir na rdo rje yid do //
NK084(yu)001:78: de yang rdo rje ni dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ste /
NK084(yu)001:80: yid ni kun tu bzang po ste /
NK084(yu)001:82: la ni bzhi ste de gnyis yul du byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:83: phyag ni don dang tshig tu rtsal lo //
NK084(yu)001:84: de ni lhag ma can gyi tshig ste /
NK084(yu)001:85: rgyud kyi don bstus snying po tsam //
NK084(yu)001:86: zhes bshad par dam bca' ba dang 'brel ba yin no //
NK084(yu)001:87: bshad par dam bca' ba ni gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:92: dam bcas pas gdul bya yal bar mi dor ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:93: bstan chos rtsom pa mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK084(yu)001:97: tshul lam thabs ji ltar bshad /
NK084(yu)001:98: bshad pa'i dgos pa ci yod pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:99: de yang gang gis bshad na /
NK084(yu)001:100: sangs rgyas gsang bas bshad do //
NK084(yu)001:101: gang bshad na zhi ba rin chen dra ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:103: phyag 'tshal nas bshad par dam bca' ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:104: dgos pa ni bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ma
NK084(yu)001:105: rig par rang gi rnam rtog gis bcings pa'i sems
NK084(yu)001:106: can rnams / rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po rgyud la skyed pa'i dgos pa yod /
NK084(yu)001:107: tshig don ni e ma'o zhes pa la sogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:108: e ma'o bde' gshegs snying po las /
NK084(yu)001:109: gzhi' rig pa'i gnas thabs bstan /
NK084(yu)001:110: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:111: ngo gang la mtshar na sems can gyi sems nyid
NK084(yu)001:112: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying por gnas pa de ma
NK084(yu)001:113: rtogs par gnas pas de la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:114: de bas na khams gsum na gnas pa'i sems can la /
NK084(yu)001:115: snying po byang chub kyi sems rang la rang chas
NK084(yu)001:116: su yod kyang nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa'i
NK084(yu)001:119: snying po byang chub kyi sems ma rtogs pa de nyid 'khor ba'i rgyur gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:120: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis bcings //
NK084(yu)001:122: rgyud pa'i rgyur gyur pa de kho na rang gi rnam rtog ste /
NK084(yu)001:123: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:124: rgyu de la rkyen ni las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis rang gi rgyud bcings nas /
NK084(yu)001:125: 'bras bu 'gro ba rigs drug gi rtog pas bcings nas thar pa'i dus med do //
NK084(yu)001:126: rang byung ye shes skyed pa'i phyir //
NK084(yu)001:127: 'bras bu ye shes skyed thabs bstan /
NK084(yu)001:128: 'gro drug nas thar dus myed pa de lta bu la /
NK084(yu)001:129: rang 'byung ye shes kyi snang ba sngar ma skyes
NK084(yu)001:130: pa de skyed pa de skyed pa'i phyir slob dpon
NK084(yu)001:131: sangs rgyas gsang bas rgyud gsang ba snying po'i don
NK084(yu)001:133: ji ltar rtsom na rgyud kyi don ces sbyar ro //
NK084(yu)001:134: rgyud kyi don bsdus snying po rtsam //
NK084(yu)001:135: rang gzog spangs pa'i phyir thus pa'i rgyud kyi khungs ba stan /
NK084(yu)001:136: rgyud ni dpal gsang ba snying po la /
NK084(yu)001:145: bdun gyi don man ngag 'dir bstus pas na /
NK084(yu)001:146: man ngag gi snying po lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:147: de bas na rgyud don gyi man ngag 'dir bsdus nas snying po rtsams so //
NK084(yu)001:148: thos bsam bsgoms la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:149: gzhi' rig pa'i gnas thabs bstan /
NK084(yu)001:150: so so skye bo rig pa'i rtsal sbyong na shes rab rnam pa gsum ni /
NK084(yu)001:151: sgra dang don yul du byas pa las skye ba yin te /
NK084(yu)001:152: de yang sgra yul du byas pa las thos pa'i shes rab skye ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:153: sgra don gnyis ka yul du byas pa las bsam pa'i shes rab skye ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:154: sgra spangs nas don b+ha zhig yul du byas pa las sgom pa'i shes rab skye'o //
NK084(yu)001:155: de'i dus su snod kyi skyon bzhi spangs te /
NK084(yu)001:160: de bas na dang po thos pa'i shes rab /
NK084(yu)001:161: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab /
NK084(yu)001:162: tha mar sgom pa'i shes rab /
NK084(yu)001:163: thos bsam sgom gsum la blo rab tu sbyangs pa byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:164: shes rab dmigs ldan rnams kyis bzung //
NK084(yu)001:165: sngon du theg pa 'og ma la blo sbyang ba bstan /
NK084(yu)001:166: de ltar shes rab gsum gyis thun mong gi theg pa la /
NK084(yu)001:169: dus da lta shes rab kyi spyan gyis blo mchog
NK084(yu)001:170: tu gyur pa'i de lta bu'i gang zag rnams kyis
NK084(yu)001:171: 'di zung zhig /de ma yin pa'i gzhan sbyangs pa
NK084(yu)001:172: sngon du ma song ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:173: shes rab dang mi ldan pa rnams kyis 'di'i don mi rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:174: de bas na snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan ces bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:175: de rnams ni sbyangs pa'i yon tan no //
NK084(yu)001:176: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK084(yu)001:177: sbyangs pa can gyi gang zag de nyid snod dang ldan par bya ba bstan /
NK084(yu)001:178: de ltar snod dang ldan par gyur pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:179: ngang ring ba chu bo'i rgyun lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:180: bzod pa khyad can thob pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:181: tshul shes pa dge slong gsang ba lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:182: tho cho dang bab chol gyi spyod pa spangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:183: rang bzhin gyis bzang ba nyi ma lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:184: sems can la snying rje chen po dang ldan pas /
NK084(yu)001:185: phyogs su 'dzin pa thams cad spangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:186: rigs ldan pas ri bo lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:187: gsang ba'i theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas /
NK084(yu)001:188: phyis theg pa dman pa la myi ldog /de lta bu la chos bstan par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:189: de rnams ni rang bzhin gyi yon tan yin no //
NK084(yu)001:190: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK084(yu)001:191: spyir na bla ma mnyes pa'i yon tan gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:192: rab shes rab kyis mnyes pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:194: tha ma longs spyod kyis mnyes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:195: rab ni theg pa 'og ma ba la blo sbyangs pas /
NK084(yu)001:196: shes rab kyi spyan dang ldan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:197: 'bring ni bla ma la lus srog 'bul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:198: tha ma ni bla ma la nor 'bul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:199: mdor na mched lcam dral dang slob dpon gyi don
NK084(yu)001:200: du rang gi lus dang longs spyod gtong nus pa
NK084(yu)001:201: ste / de lta bu'i gang zag la man ngag sbyin no //
NK084(yu)001:202: des ni bla ma mnyes pa'i yon dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:203: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK084(yu)001:204: dbang sgo yon gyis 'byed pa bstan /
NK084(yu)001:205: spyir ni slob dpon la drug ste /
NK084(yu)001:208: dbang skur ba'i dbang skur byas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:209: nyams chag snyan chen lta bu skong ba'i dang /
NK084(yu)001:210: shes rgyud bshad pa 'grol ba'i dang /
NK084(yu)001:211: man ngag gter lung gi slob dpon las /
NK084(yu)001:212: 'dir rdo rje slob dpon de la rdo rje slob dpon gyi lus ngag yid gsum /
NK084(yu)001:213: rdzas dang yo byad shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis mnyes par ma byas shing /
NK084(yu)001:214: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK084(yu)001:215: chos sgo dbang gis 'byed pa bstan /
NK084(yu)001:218: phyi'i dbang bcu ni phan dbang dang /
NK084(yu)001:219: nang dbang ni nus pa'i dbang lnga dang /
NK084(yu)001:220: gsang ba'i dbang ni zab mo'i dbang gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:221: dbang bco' brgyad po rim par thob par ma byas na zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:222: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK084(yu)001:223: dbang rim par nod pa ba stan /
NK084(yu)001:224: dbang ma thob par gsang ba bla na myed pa'i don la nyan pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:227: gzhan gyi slob dpon byed par rtsom pa rnams ni /
NK084(yu)001:228: gsang sngags la ra chod dang /
NK084(yu)001:231: rab tu gces par gdams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:233: de rnams ma byas na skyon che bar bstan /
NK084(yu)001:234: dang por bla ma mnyes par ma byas /
NK084(yu)001:236: tha mar ra chod dang gzu' lums su gyur pas na /
NK084(yu)001:237: tshe 'dir byas pa rnams ni 'bras bu myed cing /
NK084(yu)001:238: phyi ma la byas pa chud zos te bka' bzhin du ma spyad pas /
NK084(yu)001:239: 'bras bu ngan song du skye bas na /
NK084(yu)001:240: bde gshegs snying po 'khor bar gnas par 'gyur ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:241: skyon che ba de bas na /
NK084(yu)001:242: 'bras bu chos sku thob pas na /
NK084(yu)001:243: rkyen bsgom bsgrub la rag las /
NK084(yu)001:244: de chos sgo la rag las /
NK084(yu)001:246: dbang sgo yon gyis slu bas na /
NK084(yu)001:247: dang po slob dpon mnyes par bya /
NK084(yu)001:249: dbang thob nas nyan bshad mthar dbyung /
NK084(yu)001:250: de mthar phyin pas 'bras bu mchog dang thun mong 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:251: de bas na shin tu skyon che bar bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:253: slob dpon mnyes par rab byas nas //
NK084(yu)001:254: dbang rnams thob par gyur pa ni //
NK084(yu)001:255: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //
NK084(yu)001:258: mnyam don dam la mnyam par kun rdzob sbyor ba dbyer med yis //
NK084(yu)001:259: mnyam par bya ba'i ngo bo bstan /
NK084(yu)001:261: don dam ma skyes par mnyam pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:262: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:263: don dam kun rdzob dbyer myed du mnyam pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:265: chos thams cad ni ye shes kyi rang bzhin te /
NK084(yu)001:266: thog ma nas chos thams cad ma skyes par mnyam ste /
NK084(yu)001:268: kun rdzob tu phung po lnga rigs lngar mnyam /
NK084(yu)001:270: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad sems dpa' sems mar mnyam /
NK084(yu)001:271: lus kyi reg bya bzhi sgo bar mnyam /
NK084(yu)001:272: nyon mongs pa drug thub par mnyam pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:274: don dam kun rdzob ngo bo gcig par mnyam par sbyong ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:275: lta ba bden pa dbyer myed /
NK084(yu)001:277: skor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub nas gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:278: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas sngags //
NK084(yu)001:279: mnyam pa'i dgos pa ba stan /
NK084(yu)001:280: de ltar chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i rang bzhin las /
NK084(yu)001:281: myi 'da' bar dus gsum du gnas na /
NK084(yu)001:282: rang bzhin lta ba'i dam tshig ste /
NK084(yu)001:283: 'bras bu de nyid mngon du byed par ma gsungs so //
NK084(yu)001:285: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK084(yu)001:286: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK084(yu)001:287: rang gi lta ba dam tshig yin //
NK084(yu)001:289: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK084(yu)001:291: don dam skye myed du mnyam /
NK084(yu)001:293: de gnyis dbyer myed du mnyam rdzogs so //
NK084(yu)001:294: de ni chen po zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:295: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i lta ba la gnas na /
NK084(yu)001:296: rten gyi gang zag gis tshe 'di nyid la mngon
NK084(yu)001:297: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa thob par 'gyur ro
NK084(yu)001:298: // 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:299: mnyam pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon bstan /
NK084(yu)001:300: de lta bu'i dam tshig las 'das na /
NK084(yu)001:301: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma yin no zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:302: chos thams cad mnyam pa chen por ma shes te /
NK084(yu)001:303: theg pa 'og ma ltar don dam kun rdzob tha
NK084(yu)001:304: dad du mar 'dzin pa ni de las 'das pa'o
NK084(yu)001:305: // de bas na tha dad kyi gnyis 'dzin gyis sangs rgyas thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:306: de bas na mnyam pa chen po'i lta bas thag chod par bya ba gal che'o //
NK084(yu)001:307: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK084(yu)001:310: rgyu rkyen 'tshogs nas 'bras bu spyad zin pa ni 'das pa'i dus /
NK084(yu)001:311: rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa las 'bras bu ma spyad pa ni da lta ba /
NK084(yu)001:312: rgyu tsam yod pa ni 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus /
NK084(yu)001:313: rgyu rkyen gang yang ma 'tshogs pa ni ma 'ongs pa'i dus so //
NK084(yu)001:314: phyogs bcu ni gnas pa rang bzhin gyi phyogs bcu dang /
NK084(yu)001:315: sgrub pa po dmyigs pas gzung ba'i phyogs bcu dang /
NK084(yu)001:316: de ltar phyogs dang dus kyis bsdus pa gang nas kyang sangs rgyas rtsal du myed par bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:317: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK084(yu)001:319: de ltar na gnas bcu dang /
NK084(yu)001:320: dus bzhir rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gzhan nas rtsal kyang /
NK084(yu)001:321: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu gzhan nas mi rnyed do //
NK084(yu)001:324: sems nyid rtogs na sangs rgyas pas //
NK084(yu)001:325: btsal ba'i thabs ji ltar rtsal na /
NK084(yu)001:326: rang gi sems nyid rig pa byang chub sems ni
NK084(yu)001:327: ye nas 'bras bu chos kyi sku'i ngo bo yin
NK084(yu)001:328: te / de'i don rtogs par mngon du gyur pa
NK084(yu)001:329: la 'bras bu thob ces gdags kyis de las gzhan
NK084(yu)001:330: du sangs rgyas ma tshol cig /sangs rgyas gzhan du
NK084(yu)001:331: ma tshol cig /mnyam pa ma rtogs pa'i skyon bstan
NK084(yu)001:332: te / / rang rig pa de las ma rtogs pa myed pa la /
NK084(yu)001:333: rig pa de las sangs rgyas gzhan du tshol na ni /
NK084(yu)001:334: rgya mtsho'i ngos nas song ste dmyigs sgyu'i chu rnyog pa dang 'dra'o //
NK084(yu)001:335: de myi snyed pa'i phyir na de las ma rtogs pa myed pa ma tshol cig ces gdams so //
NK084(yu)001:336: gang zhig glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK084(yu)001:338: dper na glang po che snyon pa 'dul ba'i dus na /
NK084(yu)001:339: skyes bu gos dmar po gon /
NK084(yu)001:341: lag pa g.yon du spos dud thogs /
NK084(yu)001:342: g.yas su lcags kyu thogs nas /
NK084(yu)001:343: glang brid nas rtsar byung tsa na lcags kyus glang sna nas bzung nas /
NK084(yu)001:344: 'bras chang blud pas glang myos pa la /
NK084(yu)001:345: dmag mang po zhon nas btul nas /
NK084(yu)001:346: de thul tsam na gzhan gyi dmag dpung 'joms pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:347: dpe' de bzhin du rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gi sems ni /
NK084(yu)001:348: glang po che snyon pa dang 'dra ste /
NK084(yu)001:350: sngags dang phyag rgyas mnyam par bzhag /ces pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:351: mnyam par bzhag la btul nas su //
NK084(yu)001:352: sngags dang phyag rgya rab bstan na //
NK084(yu)001:355: 'khrul pa'i sems glang po dang 'dra ba de la /
NK084(yu)001:356: bla ma dam pa'i gdam ngag lcags kyu dang 'dra bas gzung nas /
NK084(yu)001:357: chos nyid rnam pa mi rtog pa'i ngang la blo mnyam par bzhag pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:358: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa de dag brtul nas /
NK084(yu)001:359: sems dang ye shes kyi phyag rgyas thams cad du snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:360: de yang sgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags kyis skyed pa'i rgyu byed /
NK084(yu)001:361: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyis gsal bar byed /
NK084(yu)001:362: bzlas pa las kyi sngags kyis bstan par byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:363: sngags de gsum gyis lha'i sku gsal ba de la ni /
NK084(yu)001:364: phyag rgya chen po bzhi dang ldan pa zhes pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:365: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)001:368: sku phyag rgya chen po rab tu bstan na dngos grub 'byung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:369: dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK084(yu)001:370: de ltar ldan na thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK084(yu)001:372: legs pa'i yon tan thams cad thob par 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:373: dgon pa chen po'i sa phyogs su //
NK084(yu)001:374: gnas kyi ring thung gi tshad bstan /
NK084(yu)001:376: dgon pa de grol yul la dpag tshad dang rgyang grags kyis ring bar gyur pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:378: bsam gyi dgra myi 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK084(yu)001:379: de bas na chen po zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:380: gnas der sa gzhi' brtag pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:382: sa gzhi' pad ma 'dab brgyad 'dra ba /
NK084(yu)001:383: sa snum la bkrag chags pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:384: gnam der phyogs brtag pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:387: nub dpung pa bzhin du 'tho ba /
NK084(yu)001:389: de bas na sa phyogs su zhes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:390: tsan dan nags dang me tog 'tshal //
NK084(yu)001:392: sa phyogs der sngon bkra shis pa'i gnas ni /
NK084(yu)001:393: tsan dan gyi nags tshal dang /
NK084(yu)001:394: mdun na me tog gi gling chags pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:395: kha dog mdzes shing bkra shis pa'i yan lag go //
NK084(yu)001:396: yid 'ong bkra shis nyams dga' ba'i //
NK084(yu)001:398: de rnams ni rnal 'byor pa 'phral nyams dga' ba yid du 'ong ba'i gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:399: grub pa thob pas bkra shis pa'i gnas ni /
NK084(yu)001:400: li yul lcang ra smug po 'am /
NK084(yu)001:402: lho brag mkhar chu lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:403: de lta bu rnal 'byor pas sgrub pa thob pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:404: bde' bar gshegs pa'i zhabs kyis bcag pa'i gnas ni /
NK084(yu)001:405: rgya gar rdo rje gdan dang /
NK084(yu)001:407: 'phags pa shing kun la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:408: bdag dbang bar chad myed pa'i gnas //
NK084(yu)001:409: gnas kyi skyon gsal ba'i bstan /
NK084(yu)001:410: gnas de bdag gi dbang du byed pas na /
NK084(yu)001:411: sa blang ba ni snang ba dang mi snang ba
NK084(yu)001:412: la rin bstsal la bdag gi dbang du bya ba
NK084(yu)001:413: dang / gnas de ha cang thag ring na rdzas kyi bar chad 'byung /
NK084(yu)001:415: lha 'dre'i lam chod na bgegs kyi bar chad 'byung
NK084(yu)001:416: bas na bkra shis la yid du 'ong ba phyi
NK084(yu)001:417: nang gi bar chad gang yang mi 'byung ba'i gnas
NK084(yu)001:418: btsal bar bya'o // bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK084(yu)001:419: sgrub pa po bdag dang 'gro ba drug gi sems can /
NK084(yu)001:420: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mtha' yas pa thams cad rnams so //
NK084(yu)001:421: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK084(yu)001:424: sku lnga ye shes lngar sangs rgyas pa yin mod kyang zhe'am /
NK084(yu)001:425: yang na rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas gcig yin kyang /
NK084(yu)001:426: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis na b+hu ta yin kyang ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:427: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba la //
NK084(yu)001:428: tshul ji ltar sems bskyed na /
NK084(yu)001:429: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i bdag dang bdag gi rtog pa'i dbang gis /
NK084(yu)001:430: khams gsum gyi 'khor ba mtho dman du 'khor bas na /
NK084(yu)001:431: da lta nyid du sku lnga ye shes lngar sangs rgyas pa'i sems bskyed do //
NK084(yu)001:432: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK084(yu)001:433: dgos pa gang gi phyir sems bskyed na /
NK084(yu)001:435: bdag kyang khams gsum las thar bar bya ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:436: bdag nyid thar nas kyang sems can thams cad thar bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:437: zhes byang chub mchog tu sku lnga ye shes lngar
NK084(yu)001:438: sangs rgyas pa yin par rtogs par sems bskyed do
NK084(yu)001:446: tshul shis pa'i gnas ni gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:447: bde' bar gshegs pa'i zhabs kyis bcag pas byin gyis brlabs pa'i gnas dang /
NK084(yu)001:448: dngos grub thob pa bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK084(yu)001:449: rang yid du 'ong bas nyams dga' ba'i gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:455: lhun grub kun 'byung gi gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:457: rang gi rig pas ngo shes te nyams dga' ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:460: dgon pa chen po ni yum la zer ba yang yod do //
NK084(yu)001:461: gzhan ma rang gi gnas skabs su ngos gzung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:462: de ni phyi'i gnas gtso' che'o //
NK084(yu)001:463: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK084(yu)001:464: chos kyi sku dang stong pa nyid kyi ye shes sems bskyed pa bstan /
NK084(yu)001:465: e ma'o ni ngam pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:466: de yang gang la ngam na chos thams cad sku
NK084(yu)001:467: lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa
NK084(yu)001:468: yin pa la / sems can rnams kyis de ltar ma rtogs pa la ngom pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:469: rmad kyi chos ni tshig ngo mtshar can las /
NK084(yu)001:470: don rmad du byung ba'i don ston pa la bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:471: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK084(yu)001:472: chos de gang gis gsungs na /
NK084(yu)001:473: rgyu bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK084(yu)001:474: sku lnga ye shes lngar lhun gyis grub pa des
NK084(yu)001:475: gsungs la sangs rgyas nyid kyi thugs kyi gnag pa
NK084(yu)001:476: yang 'di yin pas na gsang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:477: skye ba myed las thams cad skyes //
NK084(yu)001:478: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK084(yu)001:479: chos thams cad kyi ngo bo stong zhing bdag myed pa de la /
NK084(yu)001:480: rgyu gang yang skye ba myed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:481: de ltar don dam par skye ba myed pas /
NK084(yu)001:482: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad rgyu las skyed pa ltar snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:483: skyes pa nyid na skye ba myed //
NK084(yu)001:484: de ltar kun rdzob tu skyes pa nyid na don
NK084(yu)001:485: dam par ma skyes pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pa
NK084(yu)001:486: ni stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang chos kyi
NK084(yu)001:488: spyir na sems bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:489: kun rdzob byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:490: don dam pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:491: kun rdzob byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:492: smon pa 'bras bur sems bskyed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:494: don dam pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:495: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK084(yu)001:496: bstan pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK084(yu)001:497: mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:498: 'dir ni kun rdzob gzhan las khyad par byas pas na /
NK084(yu)001:499: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed /
NK084(yu)001:500: don dam pa 'od gsal mngon du byas pas na ye shes lngar sems bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:501: 'di lnga don dam kun rdzob dbyer myed ston par 'dug pas 'dabs so zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:502: rtsam gzhi so so las rtsam bya tha dad par dang /
NK084(yu)001:503: brjod bya so so la don so sor ston pa'i tshig yin no //
NK084(yu)001:504: e ma'o me long lta bu'i ye shes dang longs
NK084(yu)001:505: skur sems bskyed pa bstan ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos
NK084(yu)001:506: // rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK084(yu)001:507: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:509: rang sems stong pa skye myed du gtan la 'bebs pa'i de kho na la ngo mtshar /
NK084(yu)001:510: de gang gi chos lugs yin na /
NK084(yu)001:511: gsang ba rmad du byung ba ma h+aa yo ga'i chos /
NK084(yu)001:512: de gang gi gsung yin na /
NK084(yu)001:513: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dpal kun tu bzang po rgyal ba drug pa'i gsung /
NK084(yu)001:514: blo dman dang theg pa 'og ma ba'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas na gsang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:515: 'gag pa myed las thams cad 'gag /chos thams cad gsal la rtog pa myed pa'am /
NK084(yu)001:516: gsal la 'gag pa myed pa yin pa de las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK084(yu)001:517: chos thams cad kyi rkyen du gyur pa 'gag pa ltar snang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:518: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang sprul pa'i skur sems bskyed pa bstan no //
NK084(yu)001:520: de ltar kun rdzob tu 'gag pa ltar snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK084(yu)001:521: don dam par 'gag pa ci yang myed do //
NK084(yu)001:523: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur sems bskyed pa yin no //
NK084(yu)001:524: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK084(yu)001:525: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK084(yu)001:526: mngon par byang chub pa'i skur sems bskyed pa bstan /
NK084(yu)001:527: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK084(yu)001:528: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:530: rang sems mnyam pa nyid chen por ston pas ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:531: de gang gi chos lugs yin na /
NK084(yu)001:532: gsang ba rmad du byung ba sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i chos /
NK084(yu)001:533: de gang gi gsung yin na /
NK084(yu)001:534: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:535: gnas pa myed las thams cad gnas //
NK084(yu)001:536: chos nyid don dam par gzung ba dang 'dzin pa myed par gnas pa yin la /
NK084(yu)001:537: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:538: gzung 'dzin gyis gnas pa ltar snang yang snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:539: gnas pa nyid la gnas pa myed //
NK084(yu)001:540: de ltar kun rdzob tu gnas pa ltar snang ba'i dus nyid na /
NK084(yu)001:541: don dam par gnas pa myed de /
NK084(yu)001:542: de nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK084(yu)001:543: ngo bo nyid kyi skur sems bskyed pa yin no //
NK084(yu)001:544: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK084(yu)001:545: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK084(yu)001:546: sprul skur sems bskyed pa bstan /
NK084(yu)001:547: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK084(yu)001:548: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:549: de yang ngo gang la mtshar na /
NK084(yu)001:550: rang sems ye shes su rtogs pa de la'o //
NK084(yu)001:551: de gang gi chos yin na /
NK084(yu)001:553: de gang gi gsung yin na /
NK084(yu)001:554: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po'i gsung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:555: dmyigs pa myed las thams cad dmyigs //
NK084(yu)001:556: chos thams cad rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid ma 'dres par mkhyen la /
NK084(yu)001:557: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid don dam par dmyigs pa med do //
NK084(yu)001:558: de las ma g.yos bzhin du chos thams cad kun
NK084(yu)001:559: rdzob tu dmyigs par shar nas snang ba yin no
NK084(yu)001:560: // dmyigs pa nyid na dmyigs pa myed //
NK084(yu)001:561: de ltar kun rdzob tu dmyigs pa'i dus nyid ni /
NK084(yu)001:562: don dam par dmyigs pa myed pa las ma g.yos pa yin no //
NK084(yu)001:563: de ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK084(yu)001:564: sprul pa'i skur sems bskyed pa yin no //
NK084(yu)001:565: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK084(yu)001:566: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar te /
NK084(yu)001:568: rang sems ye shes rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:569: de gsang ba ma h+aa yo ga'i chos yin no //
NK084(yu)001:570: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK084(yu)001:572: lta ba ngan pa'i dri ma dang bral bas sangs la /
NK084(yu)001:573: ye shes mtha' dbus myed par rgyas pas na rgyas la /
NK084(yu)001:574: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag po yin pas na kun /
NK084(yu)001:575: rtogs dka' bas na gsang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:577: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis bdag dang gzhan
NK084(yu)001:578: gyi don thams cad grub cing mthar phyin par mdzad
NK084(yu)001:579: kyang / don dam par bdag dang gzhan gyi don
NK084(yu)001:580: la sprul pas phar 'gro ba dang tshur 'ong ba
NK084(yu)001:581: kyang / myed do // kun rdzob tu sprul pa phar 'gro ba dang tshur 'ong bar snang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:583: de ltar rtogs tsam nyid na don dam par 'gro
NK084(yu)001:584: 'ong myed pa ni bya ba nan tan gyi ye
NK084(yu)001:585: shes dang / rdo rje'i skur sems bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:586: bsgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK084(yu)001:588: thun mong gi bsgrub pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:589: thun mong ma yin pa'i bsgrub pa las /
NK084(yu)001:591: ting nge 'dzin myed na 'bras bu mi 'gyur bas /
NK084(yu)001:592: de'i phyir gtso bor ting nge 'dzin kho na basngagasa pa yin pas so //
NK084(yu)001:595: de bas na mchog dang thun mong gi sgrub thabs thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:596: ting 'dzin 'dir 'grub par byed pa yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:598: gser 'gyur sman dang mun sel bzhin //
NK084(yu)001:600: dper na lcags la gser 'gyur gyi rtsi gtang na lcags gser du 'gyur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:601: dug la sman ma ki ta gtab na dug sman du 'gyur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:602: mun pa la sgron me byung na mun pa sel ba bzhin du /
NK084(yu)001:603: rtog pa'i dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK084(yu)001:606: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa de bzhin nyid
NK084(yu)001:607: kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pas rtog pa thams cad chos
NK084(yu)001:608: nyid du 'gyur / ye shes sgyu ma'i ting nge
NK084(yu)001:609: 'dzin thams cad du kun tu snang bar bsgoms pas
NK084(yu)001:610: nyid du 'gyur / / phyogs gcig pa'i mun pa sel /
NK084(yu)001:611: sku dang ye shes dbyer myed phyag rgya rgyu ting
NK084(yu)001:612: du bsgoms pas phung po khams dang skye mched gnas
NK084(yu)001:613: 'gyur ba'o // de phyir ting 'dzin rim par bsgom //
NK084(yu)001:614: gtan tshigs gang gis gdams na /
NK084(yu)001:616: de ting la sogs pa gong ma rnams gsal ba'i ting la 'og ma rim par bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:617: dngos rnams nyid na dngos myed pas //
NK084(yu)001:618: phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos po sna tshogs su snang ba 'di /
NK084(yu)001:619: gzhan ma yin te rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid rang snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:620: byang chub kyi sems nyid snang ba'i dus na rang gi ngo bo cir yang ma grub pas /
NK084(yu)001:621: snang ba'i dngos por yang ma grub ste myed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:622: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK084(yu)001:623: dper na 'tshal dmar na khu ba yang dmar ba ltar /
NK084(yu)001:624: dngos po'i rtog pa ma grub pas /
NK084(yu)001:627: rtog pa dang tha snyad thams cad rang bzhin gyis bral ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:629: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK084(yu)001:630: ma nor ba'i de bzhin nyid /
NK084(yu)001:631: dngos po myed pas chos kyi dbyings /
NK084(yu)001:632: ma bcos pa yin pas ye shes /
NK084(yu)001:633: de thams cad du khyab par gnas pa yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:634: de phyir dngos po dngos myed do //
NK084(yu)001:635: mtha' dang dbus myed de kho na chos kyi dbyings so //
NK084(yu)001:636: dngos por snang ba dngos myed do //
NK084(yu)001:637: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin la drug ste /
NK084(yu)001:638: sbyang bya ni shi ba rnam rtog myed spangs so //
NK084(yu)001:639: sbyong byed ni de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin no //
NK084(yu)001:640: ngo bo ni stong pa chen po'o //
NK084(yu)001:641: rnam grangs ni ma nor ba'i de bzhin nyid /
NK084(yu)001:642: ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK084(yu)001:643: dngos po myed pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK084(yu)001:644: gzhan ma yin pa'i de bzhin nyid do //
NK084(yu)001:645: bsgom thabs ni stong pa nyid mtha' brgyad da nga bral ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:646: 'bras bu ni chos kyi sku thob pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:647: de bzhin nyid ni spros myed kyang //
NK084(yu)001:648: de bzhin nyid des thams cad la khyab pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:649: snang ba'i phyir kun tu zhes bya la /
NK084(yu)001:650: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK084(yu)001:651: de lta bu'i don ma rtogs pa'i sems can la
NK084(yu)001:652: snying rje chen po phyogs ris myed pa bsgom pa'o
NK084(yu)001:653: // sems can kun la snying rtse'i phyir //
NK084(yu)001:654: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK084(yu)001:655: chos kyi dbyings nam mkha' dang 'dra bar kun la khyab la /
NK084(yu)001:656: snying rje chen po yang de ltar bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:657: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin la drug la /
NK084(yu)001:658: sbyang bya ni bar do'i snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:659: sbyong byed ni kun tu snang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:660: ngo bo ni ye shes sgyu ma'o //
NK084(yu)001:661: rnam grangs ni kun tu snang zhes bya /
NK084(yu)001:662: ye shes sgyu ma zhes bya /
NK084(yu)001:663: 'tshams sbyor chen po'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:665: ma h+aa yo ga chos nyid ye shes sgyu ma bsgom la /
NK084(yu)001:666: a nu yo ga ba rang gi smin 'tshams su
NK084(yu)001:667: 'od dmar smug tshon gang ba las 'od 'phros pas
NK084(yu)001:668: / 'jig rten thams cad 'od kyis khengs par bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:669: 'dir ni chos nyid ye shes sgyu mar bsgom pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:671: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku 'thob bo //
NK084(yu)001:672: gzhi' rtsa myed pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK084(yu)001:676: mtshon pa tsam du sems zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:679: brten pa dang gnas pa'i tha snyad dang bral ba'i /
NK084(yu)001:680: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK084(yu)001:682: de nyid dngos po yod myed gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin te /
NK084(yu)001:683: rig pa byang chub kyi sems rten gzhi'i dang bral ba nyid do //
NK084(yu)001:684: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin to //
NK084(yu)001:685: rig pa sems nyid rten gzhi' dang bral ba nyid
NK084(yu)001:686: gnas kyi ye shes rang snang ba ni a dkar
NK084(yu)001:687: po'o // a'i sgra ni chos nyid skye ba myed pa'i don bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:688: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK084(yu)001:690: a'i dbyibs las yi ge thams cad 'byung ba'i phyir na yi ge a'i mchog ste /
NK084(yu)001:691: de la dmyigs pa rtse gcig tu brtan pa la sgom pa zhes bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:692: a rab tu brtan 'gyur a dkar las /
NK084(yu)001:693: rtsa ba'i yi ge a las spros bsdu' bya bar bstan /
NK084(yu)001:694: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin a dkar po de rkyen dbang
NK084(yu)001:695: du mi 'gro ba brtan pa dang 'od spros te
NK084(yu)001:696: / a ni chos nyid kyi rang bzhin rig pa byang chub sems so //
NK084(yu)001:698: rab tu dmyigs kyis mngon par na'o //
NK084(yu)001:699: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin la drug ste /
NK084(yu)001:700: sbyang bya ni mngal du 'jug pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:701: sbyong byed ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK084(yu)001:702: ngo bo ni yi ge a'o //
NK084(yu)001:706: bsgom thabs ni a dkar po rgya skar ma la sa pa la khar shar ba lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:709: yan lag gi yi ge dbyangs dang gsal byed la spro bsdu bya bar bstan no //
NK084(yu)001:710: gzhi' bo'i a de las a 'phra mo mang po phar la spros pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:711: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal 'gyur nas //
NK084(yu)001:712: yi ge a phyogs bcur spros pas /
NK084(yu)001:713: phyogs bcu as gang nas yi ge a gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:716: 'od zer gyis dngos por snang ba thams cad sregs sbyangs nas /
NK084(yu)001:717: chos thams cad don dam pa'i bden par byas nas /
NK084(yu)001:718: tshur la 'dus pas a'i gzhi mo la thim mo //
NK084(yu)001:719: de ltar byas pas phar la spros kyang a chung du ma song /
NK084(yu)001:720: tshur bsdus kyang cher ma song bas bsdus kyang 'phel 'grib myed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:721: de las ming tshogs 'bar ba kun //
NK084(yu)001:722: a de la ming gi yi ge ni /
NK084(yu)001:725: a +aa i +ai la sogs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:726: de dag yid la gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:727: kha dog 'od zer 'bar bar bsgom pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:728: de ni kun rdzob bden pa'i yi ge'o //
NK084(yu)001:729: spro zhing bsdu' ba'ang de bzhin no //
NK084(yu)001:730: a las yi ge dbyibs dang 'od zer can du 'phros pas /
NK084(yu)001:731: snod bcud sbyangs pas a chung du ma song /
NK084(yu)001:732: bsdus pas kyang cher ma song /
NK084(yu)001:734: de yang chos nyid yin pas 'phel 'grib dang bral lo //
NK084(yu)001:735: 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK084(yu)001:736: yi ge 'di ni don skye ba med pa'i yi ge rtags ni yi ge a /
NK084(yu)001:737: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad 'byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:738: bstan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK084(yu)001:739: ting nge 'dzin las byung ba ni sku dang ye
NK084(yu)001:740: shes thams cad kyi 'byung ba'i rgyu'am skyed pa'i rkyen
NK084(yu)001:742: de las rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas rten //
NK084(yu)001:743: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gsal zhing rtan pa de las /
NK084(yu)001:744: rgyal ba rnams bzhugs pa'i rten nam gnas su gyur par bsgom pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:745: dbang chen dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsgom //
NK084(yu)001:746: 'byung ba lnga rang bzhin gyis sangs rgyas pas na dbang chen no //
NK084(yu)001:747: e nam ka yam rlung bam chu sum gser lam /
NK084(yu)001:748: ri rab b+h+r+aum bi sha bi shud d+he /
NK084(yu)001:749: rin po che'i ri rab kyi steng du /
NK084(yu)001:750: yi ge b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK084(yu)001:751: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal ba /
NK084(yu)001:752: nang nas bltas na phyi gsal ba /
NK084(yu)001:753: gang yang mi sgrib pa'i rang bzhin can no //
NK084(yu)001:754: 'byung ba rim rtsegs pa yang drug ste /
NK084(yu)001:755: sbyang bya ni snod kyi 'jig rten no //
NK084(yu)001:756: sbyong byed ni 'byung ba rim rtsegs so //
NK084(yu)001:763: de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK084(yu)001:764: e gru gsum chos kyi 'byung gnas /
NK084(yu)001:765: phyi dkar la nang dmar ba yangs shing rgya che ba gcig bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:767: yum kun tu bzang mo'i ba ga rnam par dag pas nang du na kun gzhi'i sbyong ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:773: nang du na phung po'i dbugs so //
NK084(yu)001:774: bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dbyibs zlum po /
NK084(yu)001:778: lus la sbyar na khrag go //
NK084(yu)001:779: sum las gser gyi sa gzhi' /
NK084(yu)001:785: yam las rin po che'i ri rab /
NK084(yu)001:794: 'phrag dog dug lnga dang yang sbyar ro //
NK084(yu)001:795: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor /
NK084(yu)001:798: yum gos dkar mo'i ba ga rnam par dag pa /
NK084(yu)001:800: phung po'i drod dang sbyar ro //
NK084(yu)001:801: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dang /
NK084(yu)001:805: bya ba grub pa ste ye shes lnga dang sbyar ro //
NK084(yu)001:806: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK084(yu)001:807: ji ltar rtogs pa bya na /
NK084(yu)001:808: dkyil rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK084(yu)001:809: 'khor bzhi bcu tham pas skor ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:810: gdul bya'i blo bsam yas kyang /
NK084(yu)001:811: blo che ba la rang bzhin lhun grub du gnas pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:812: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:813: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK084(yu)001:814: gang gis rtogs par bya na /
NK084(yu)001:815: sgrub pa po rten gyi gang zag blo mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:816: des chos thams cad ye nas lam dang gnyen pos ma bcos pa /
NK084(yu)001:817: sku dang ye shes su sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du /
NK084(yu)001:818: rgyud kyi don rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtogs par byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:819: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus rtags te //
NK084(yu)001:821: mtshon byed ni 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus dang lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:822: mtshon bya ni ye shes lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:823: dbus chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK084(yu)001:826: nub so so kun rtog /byang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:827: de yang phyogs mthun pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:832: rtogs pa'i don ci zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:833: b+hu ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang po rang la lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:835: rgya mtsho las gza' skar 'char ba bzhin du /
NK084(yu)001:836: dus gcig la rdzogs par bsgom pa yin no //
NK084(yu)001:837: spyir na gzhal yas khang la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:838: chos nyid rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK084(yu)001:843: rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:847: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:849: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:850: de'i steng du byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK084(yu)001:851: mchod pa tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:852: de las 'dir rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:853: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK084(yu)001:855: dbus lte ba zlum po chos kyi dbyings te mthing ka'o //
NK084(yu)001:856: rtsibs bzhi ni ye shes bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:857: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:858: spros pa myed pa'i mu khyud zlum po rdo rje rtsigs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:859: thams cad dbang du bsdus pa'i rtsibs 'chan dmar po /
NK084(yu)001:860: 'phrin las bzhi dang ldan pas na gru chad ljang khu'o //
NK084(yu)001:861: lhag pa'i ye shes blo 'bur can //
NK084(yu)001:862: ye shes re re la yang ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rtags su /
NK084(yu)001:869: de yang ye shes gzhan las khyad par du gyur te spags nas lhag pa'i brtags can no //
NK084(yu)001:870: gru chad bzhis brgyan bar khyams dang /
NK084(yu)001:871: 'phrin las bzhi'i gru chad bzhis dbus kyi pho brang la rgyan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:872: dbyer med pa'i don la mkhas pas bden bar tshul gcig tu 'dus te /
NK084(yu)001:873: don dam pa kun rdzob dbyer med pas na bar khyams phyogs mthun no //
NK084(yu)001:874: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK084(yu)001:875: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs bstan /
NK084(yu)001:876: rang rig pa nyid la sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i
NK084(yu)001:877: yon tan thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su
NK084(yu)001:878: / phyi'i dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:879: de yang stong pa nyid dang /
NK084(yu)001:882: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'i phyir na sgo bzhi yod pa /
NK084(yu)001:883: theg pa rim pa brgyad yod pa'i gnas su gyur pas rta babs brgyad yod pa /
NK084(yu)001:884: stong nyid mi shigs pa'i rtags su rdo rje'i ra bas skor ba /
NK084(yu)001:885: gdug pa can 'joms pa'i rtags su /
NK084(yu)001:886: me dpung 'bar bas 'khrigs pa can no //
NK084(yu)001:887: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK084(yu)001:889: gzhal yas khang de la pan tsa ra ga'i rtsig pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:890: rin chen pha gu'i bar na /
NK084(yu)001:891: 'dod yon snam bu dmar po la /
NK084(yu)001:892: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mo sprin phung bzhin du 'khrigs pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:893: snang la rang bzhin myed pa gsal la mi sgrib pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:894: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis rgyan //
NK084(yu)001:896: gzhal yas khang gi bdag po ni rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK084(yu)001:897: 'o na dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan ni lha 'gro ba'i ci ste zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:898: spyir rgyan la mang du yod kyang 'dir rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK084(yu)001:899: gzhal yas khang dang lha la snga phyi myed la /
NK084(yu)001:900: 'dir snga phyi byung ba ni gdul bya'i bsam pa la dgongs nas /
NK084(yu)001:901: gdul bya blo chung bas dus skad cig la mi lcogs par /
NK084(yu)001:902: rim pas smos pa yin te /
NK084(yu)001:903: de bas na sngon la gzhal yas khang bskyed nas /
NK084(yu)001:904: de nas lha phyi la bskyed pa la dgongs na rgyan zer ro //
NK084(yu)001:905: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi cha byad can /
NK084(yu)001:906: sprul pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi cha byad can /
NK084(yu)001:907: sprul pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis rgyan zer ro //
NK084(yu)001:908: yang na gzhal yas khang gi rgyan du lha 'gyur te /
NK084(yu)001:909: khang stong la bdag pos rgyan pa lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:910: seng ge gdan ba stan pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:911: dbus shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pas myi 'jigs pa bzhi thob pas seng ge gdan no //
NK084(yu)001:912: glang chen shar du bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pas mi 'gyur ba'i rtags su /
NK084(yu)001:913: stobs bcu mnga' bas glang po'i gdan dkar po'o //
NK084(yu)001:914: rta dang lho sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin pas rdzu
NK084(yu)001:915: 'phrul rkang pa bzhi mtshon pa'i rtags su rta mchog
NK084(yu)001:918: nub tu tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK084(yu)001:919: rtags su dbang bcu mtshon pa mdzes pa'i khyung rma
NK084(yu)001:922: rtags kyi che ba bcom pa'i gdan ni /
NK084(yu)001:923: sems can brgyad brgyad mjug ma nang du snol nas gdan 'og na rna bas chos nyan pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:924: de yang byang chub sems dpa' shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong bas lus gdan du phul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:925: sa'i khyad par sgrod pa'i gdan ni /
NK084(yu)001:927: bcu gnyis ma chags pad ma can dang /
NK084(yu)001:928: bcu gsum yi ge tshogs chen gyi sa non pas /
NK084(yu)001:930: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan ni /
NK084(yu)001:931: 'og gzhi' chos kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'am /
NK084(yu)001:932: rin po che'i khri rkang la dgos 'dod 'byung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:933: 'og gzhi' 'khor lo la chos kyis 'gro ba 'dul bar bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:934: de bas na don dang rtags su ldan pa'i gdan lnga rtsegs so //
NK084(yu)001:935: sems dpa' sems ma la nyi zla pad ma'o //
NK084(yu)001:936: thub pa la pad rkyang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:937: sgo ba la rdo rje brag gi steng na nyi ma rkyang pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:938: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK084(yu)001:939: byang du brtson 'grus kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i rtags su 'phrin las sna tshogs pa mtshon pas /
NK084(yu)001:940: shang shang nam mkha' lding gi gdan /
NK084(yu)001:941: lus po ser la gshog pa g.yur snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:942: nyi shes rab stong pa mtshon pa nyi ma'i gdan no //
NK084(yu)001:943: zla thabs ma 'gags pa mtshon pa zla ba'i gdan no //
NK084(yu)001:944: pad ma skyon gyis ma gos pa mtshon pa gdan sna tshogs pa'i pad ma'o //
NK084(yu)001:946: dgos 'dod sna tshogs 'byung ba rin po che 'bar ba'i gdan no //
NK084(yu)001:947: a ni skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK084(yu)001:948: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi a de dbus kyi gdan stengs su babs pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:949: a'i don chos nyid skye ba myed pa yin la /
NK084(yu)001:950: rtags kun tu bzang po'i sa bon no //
NK084(yu)001:951: ngo bo de bzhin nyid kun gzhi'i chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin no //
NK084(yu)001:952: k+sha ni thugs kyi ye shes shar //
NK084(yu)001:953: a de las k+sha g.yas su 'phros pa'i don ni /
NK084(yu)001:954: thugs rig pa'i ye shes shar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:955: rtags kun tu bzang po'i sa bon no //
NK084(yu)001:956: ngo bo yid rang 'byung gi ye shes bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs so //
NK084(yu)001:957: de las cho 'phrul gsum gyi skyed //
NK084(yu)001:958: a dang k+sha gnyis su gsal ba gsung yig 'bru'i cho ga'o //
NK084(yu)001:959: de 'phro 'dus pas rdo rje dang dril bu gnyis su gyur /
NK084(yu)001:960: pa ni thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho ga'o //
NK084(yu)001:961: de 'phro 'dus pa las sku phra mor gyur pa
NK084(yu)001:962: las sku phra mor gyur pa ni sku yongs su
NK084(yu)001:964: de 'phro 'dus pa las sngags brjod pas kun bzang yab yum du bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:965: kun bzang mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK084(yu)001:966: yum 'gyur mnyam rdzogs pad mo'i dkyil //
NK084(yu)001:968: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsita h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK084(yu)001:969: kun tu bzang po phyag gnyis zhabs gnyis dkyil krung mnyam bzhag tu bzhugs pa /
NK084(yu)001:970: rgyan thams cad kyis rgyan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:971: sku mthing ka phyag mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can dgongs pa mnyam bzhag tu bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:972: sor mo so sor gsal ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:973: ye shes 'phro zhing gsal ba'i don yin no //
NK084(yu)001:974: phyag rgya chen po'i sku gnyis rdzogs //
NK084(yu)001:975: a a a badz+ra sa t+wa sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK084(yu)001:977: yum kun tu bzang mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK084(yu)001:978: sku mthing ka yab la 'khril ba zhabs pad ma'i dkyil krung du bzhugs pa /
NK084(yu)001:979: yab dang sku mnyam par rdzogs pa /
NK084(yu)001:980: nyes pa'i skyon dang bral ba'i don no //
NK084(yu)001:981: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK084(yu)001:982: sku dang gsung thugs dang kyi rdo rje'i bdag po yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:983: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid chen po yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:984: kun tu bzang por ye nas yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK084(yu)001:985: rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid dpal kun tu bzang por bskyed pa de yang /
NK084(yu)001:986: 'phral la byas pa lta bu myin te /
NK084(yu)001:987: ye nas sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin /
NK084(yu)001:988: dpal kun tu bzang po yin pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:989: bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:990: bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir na bdag
NK084(yu)001:991: gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba ni
NK084(yu)001:992: lnga ste / sangs rgyas gang dang sbyar ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:993: don gang dang mthun pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:997: sangs rgyas ni rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas dang sbyar /
NK084(yu)001:998: de yang bdag rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs
NK084(yu)001:999: rgyas yin pas na rang bzhin gyi lhar bsgom pa'o
NK084(yu)001:1004: dper na 'jig rten srid pa'i mes po lha gshed bu dang gshed la yin pa ltar /
NK084(yu)001:1005: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mes po rang bzhin lhun
NK084(yu)001:1006: grub kyi sangs rgyas te dpal kun tu bzang po'o
NK084(yu)001:1008: ma h+aa yo ga a ti yo ga dang sbyar nas 'jug pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1010: rig pa ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don de rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1011: ye shes gang rtogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1012: rig pa rang gsal gyi ye shes thob pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1013: 'o na bdag dpal kun tu bzang po yab yum gnyis po sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin na /
NK084(yu)001:1014: 'bu ta bzhi bcu po de lha 'phral byung gi sangs rgyas yin nam zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:1015: de byas na blo bur ba yin pas don mi grub pas mi 'thad do //
NK084(yu)001:1016: de ma yin na sngon gyi sangs rgyas zhes ci la gdags zhe na zhes dris pa na /
NK084(yu)001:1017: de'i lan du de ni 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:1018: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK084(yu)001:1019: ye ji bzhin pa'i kun tu bzang por ma shes na /
NK084(yu)001:1020: rig pa sangs rgyas su thag mi chod pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1022: rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas /
NK084(yu)001:1023: rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas myed na /
NK084(yu)001:1025: bde' gshegs rgyun chad pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:1026: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1027: bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1029: 'bu ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sngar phyi myed kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1030: gdul bya'i blo dang mthun par bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1031: de bas na bdag sangs rgyas nas gzhan don byed pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1032: 'bu ta nyid la 'bu ta nyid kyis don bskul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1033: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin las //
NK084(yu)001:1034: yab thabs kyi rang bzhin kun tu bzang po'i mkha' ni /
NK084(yu)001:1035: rdo rje rtse lnga pa mchu' sbubs su +amo gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1036: yum shes rab kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' ni pad
NK084(yu)001:1037: ma 'dab ma brgyad par bsgoms pa'i lte ba la
NK084(yu)001:1038: bsam / de ltar yab yum gnyis su myed par
NK084(yu)001:1039: rol pa'i byang chub sems sprin lta bu zag pa
NK084(yu)001:1040: myed pa'i thig le bde ba chen po las /
NK084(yu)001:1041: byang chub sems tshogs rgyu 'khor lo //
NK084(yu)001:1042: yab yum rol pa'i byang chub sems kyi tshogs su byung ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:1043: lha bskyed pa'i rgyu 'khor lo ltar 'byung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:1044: 'bras bu rgyal ba smin grub byed //
NK084(yu)001:1045: de lta bu'i yi ge rnams la /
NK084(yu)001:1046: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags brjod na /
NK084(yu)001:1048: 'bu ta rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su smin cing grub par byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1049: ngo mtshar ming tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK084(yu)001:1050: de las rgyu yi ge 'bras bu sangs rgyas su grub pa ni ngo mtshar to //
NK084(yu)001:1052: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni grangs kyi rnam grangs so //
NK084(yu)001:1053: yi ge 'di rnams la spyi don gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:1056: yi ge lha dang ngo sbyar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1057: lha dang ngo sbyar ba ni gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:1058: phyi rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su ngo sprad pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1059: nang rtsa gnas kyi thig le dang sbyar ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1060: gsang ba yab yum gyi byang sems dang sbyar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1061: de yang gzhi thig ler gnas pa las /
NK084(yu)001:1062: byang sems yi ger babs pa las lhar bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1064: skye ba myed pa'i don kun gzhi' chos kyi dbyings /
NK084(yu)001:1065: yum kun tu bzang mo'i rgyu'o //
NK084(yu)001:1066: ka sa'i snying po kha phyag rdor ga spyan ras gzigs g+ha nam mkha' snying po nga /
NK084(yu)001:1069: la se ma tsa nir ti ma tsha g+hir ti
NK084(yu)001:1070: ma dza ma le ma dz+ha stobs po che nya
NK084(yu)001:1071: / lce rtse dang khog pa las 'byung /
NK084(yu)001:1072: rnam snang ta myi bskyod pa tha rin 'byung da snang mtha' d+ha don grub na /
NK084(yu)001:1074: sangs rgyas spyan ta dbyings phyug ma tha ma ma
NK084(yu)001:1075: ki da gos dkar mo d+ha dam tshig sgrol ma
NK084(yu)001:1077: byam pa pa sgrib sel pha kun bzang ba 'jam dpal b+ha rta mgrin ma /
NK084(yu)001:1078: ya du pe spos ma ra spus pe me tog ma la a lo ke mar me ma wa /
NK084(yu)001:1080: sha lcags kyu ma sha zhags pa ma sa lcags sgrog ma ha /
NK084(yu)001:1082: k+sha yid kun tu bzang po /
NK084(yu)001:1083: i lha'i thub pa +ai lha ma yin gyi /
NK084(yu)001:1087: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa lus kyi reg bya gzhi' reg par 'dus pa yi ge gnyis 'byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1088: a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK084(yu)001:1089: yi ge a ni sems can la gnas pa'i dus kun gzhi' /
NK084(yu)001:1090: don du na chos kyi ye shes /
NK084(yu)001:1091: yi ge thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1092: a las yi ge sna tshogs pa 'byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1094: ka la sogs pa'i bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK084(yu)001:1095: ka la sogs pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su 'byung ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:1097: gzhi'i yi ge a las 'byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1098: sgra'i ming gis thams cad sdus //
NK084(yu)001:1099: de yang yi ge las sgra 'byung /
NK084(yu)001:1102: tshig las don gsal zhing rtogs pas tshig las don byung nas des chos thams cad bsdus pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1103: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges //
NK084(yu)001:1104: rgyu'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis nyid /
NK084(yu)001:1105: 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su rdzogs par 'byung la /
NK084(yu)001:1106: rgyal ba de dag yang longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK084(yu)001:1107: 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po ltar 'byung ba ni
NK084(yu)001:1108: / sprul pa'i sku lta bu yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1109: de la rkyen gyi sngags kyis bskul //
NK084(yu)001:1110: kun tu bzang po yab yum gyi mkha' gsang nas gdan stengs su yi ge 'phros pa las /
NK084(yu)001:1111: h'u badz+ra 'drig las skyed pa'i rkyen gyi sngags kyis skul bas /
NK084(yu)001:1112: lha so so'i sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK084(yu)001:1114: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid dang bzhi las /
NK084(yu)001:1115: 'di rnams gsang ba sgyu 'phrul dra ba yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1116: dra ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs gsal //
NK084(yu)001:1117: 'di rnams ni rnal 'byor sgyu 'phrul dra ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:1118: chos nyid kyi gzugs brnyan yum gyi skur 'byung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1119: ye shes kyi gzugs brnyan yab kyi skur 'byung ba gnyis /
NK084(yu)001:1120: ye nas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed par 'brel ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1121: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor na rig pa mngon sum du gsal ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1123: don dam par chos nyid 'dus ma byas pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1124: kun rdzob tsam du lha'i sku 'dus byas ltar snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1126: de kho na kun rdzob don dam par snang yang /
NK084(yu)001:1127: don gyi ngo bo la bden pa dbyer myed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK084(yu)001:1128: dbang myed rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'i mthu' chen yin //
NK084(yu)001:1130: rgyu sa bon la rkyen chu lud 'dzom na 'bras bu rang dbang myed par 'byung ba ltar /
NK084(yu)001:1131: rgyu zag myed kyi byang chub sems yi ger snang ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1132: rkyen bskyed pa'i sngags kyis nus pa 'tshogs na /
NK084(yu)001:1133: 'bras bu lha'i sku rang dbang myed par 'byung ste /
NK084(yu)001:1134: gsang sngags gsang ba'i nus mthu' yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1135: de yan cad kyis bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pa'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1136: bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1137: rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1138: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba la lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:1139: sangs rgyas gang dang sbyar ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1140: don gang dang mthun pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1142: don gang thob cing rtogs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1144: sangs rgyas gang dang sbyar na /
NK084(yu)001:1145: rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas dang sbyar /
NK084(yu)001:1146: de yang rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1148: pha mas bu tsha bskyed pa dang 'dra'o //
NK084(yu)001:1150: ma h+aa yo ga'i a nu yo ga nas 'jug go //
NK084(yu)001:1152: rang 'byung gii ye shes chen po rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1153: rang rig pa la rang gis rtogs pa mngon du gyur /
NK084(yu)001:1154: rgyud dag pa'i kun tu bzang por byas /
NK084(yu)001:1155: rig pa dang rtogs pa dbyer myed /
NK084(yu)001:1157: rang rig pa sangs rgyas yin pa la /
NK084(yu)001:1159: de'i sras su bdag byas pa las 'byung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:1160: de nas bcom ldan dgyes chen rigs //
NK084(yu)001:1161: dkyil 'khor dang po bskyed pa de nas bcom ldan
NK084(yu)001:1162: 'das kun tu bzang po rigs kyi bdag po yab
NK084(yu)001:1163: yum gnyis su myed pa las so //
NK084(yu)001:1164: lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir //
NK084(yu)001:1165: lhun gyis grub par yod kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1166: rang bzhin lhun grub de rtogs pa mngon du gyur par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:1167: rang snang dbyer myed dkyil 'khor la //
NK084(yu)001:1169: rang snang rig pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis dbyer myed pa'i dkyil 'khor du bya ba'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:1170: rtogs pas lhun grub tu bya ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1171: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bdag bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1172: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK084(yu)001:1173: gzhi rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor de /
NK084(yu)001:1174: rkyen 'jug pa'i lam gyi mtshan nyid kyis nyams su blangs la /
NK084(yu)001:1175: gzhi' de rang gi blo la mnyam par sbyar ro //
NK084(yu)001:1176: rang gi ngang tshul de bzung nas //
NK084(yu)001:1177: bskul tshig 'di yang rab tu brjod //
NK084(yu)001:1178: dbus kyi gtso' bo'i thugs ka nas rang gi rnam
NK084(yu)001:1179: par smin pa'i lus 'di 'dra ba'i tshangs pa phru
NK084(yu)001:1180: gu'i cha byad can gcig byung nas so //
NK084(yu)001:1181: de byung nas bar khyams nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la skor ba byas nas /
NK084(yu)001:1182: nub sgor 'dug ste rkyang phyag lan gsum 'tshal nas /
NK084(yu)001:1183: spus mo btsugs te dkyil 'khor gyi lha la gsol ba lan gsum 'debs pa 'di skad do //
NK084(yu)001:1184: +amo ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK084(yu)001:1185: yon tan 'phrin las rmad po che //
NK084(yu)001:1186: rang 'byung ye shes kyi ngo bo dpal kun tu bzang po ni /
NK084(yu)001:1187: thams cad du dbang bskur ba'i phyir na rgyal po'o //
NK084(yu)001:1188: sku'i rigs rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK084(yu)001:1189: gsung gi rigs snang ba mtha' yas /
NK084(yu)001:1190: thugs kyi rigs mi bskyod pa /
NK084(yu)001:1192: 'phrin las kyi rigs don yod grub pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1193: de yang rgyal ba lnga so sor byung ba ni ma yin te /
NK084(yu)001:1194: rgyal ba gcig las yon tan sku gsung thugs 'phrin
NK084(yu)001:1195: las re re dang ldan pas na rmad po che
NK084(yu)001:1196: zhes bya'o // da lta nyid du mnyam sbyor bas //
NK084(yu)001:1197: de lta bu de bdag la dus da lta nyid du khyed dang dbyer myed par sbyor bas na /
NK084(yu)001:1198: dus phyi ma la mi ltos pa'i dus da lta nyid du sbyor ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1199: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /khyed kyis phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /ces pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1200: ji ltar bdag rang bzhin lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas dang /
NK084(yu)001:1201: khyed rtogs pa mngon 'gyur gyi sangs rgyas gnyis dbyer myed par gyur la /
NK084(yu)001:1202: bdag nyid kyang rtogs pa mngon gyur gyi sangs rgyas su sbyor cig pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1203: de ltar gsol ba btab pas /
NK084(yu)001:1204: dkyil 'khor gyi lha yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK084(yu)001:1205: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub kyi sems rno la myur ba grangs myed pa byung bas /
NK084(yu)001:1206: bdag gi lus kyi sdig pa thams cad bya sgro la mes sregs pa bzhin du sbyangs nas /
NK084(yu)001:1207: sems gser zhun ma bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1208: de la lha rnams kyis gzigs te /
NK084(yu)001:1209: sems rten gyi gnas su yi ge +amo +aa h'u gsum 'phros pas /
NK084(yu)001:1210: 'od kyi rang bzhin lha'i sems de yi ge gsum du gyur to //
NK084(yu)001:1211: yi ge yang 'phro 'dus pas h'u du thim /
NK084(yu)001:1212: des bar khyams nas skor ba lan gsum byas nas /
NK084(yu)001:1215: rdo rje lam du byung nas /
NK084(yu)001:1216: yum gyi mkha' la babs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1217: thabs dang shes yum rab gnyis myed sbyar pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:1218: ye shes lha'i 'od zer gyis bdag gi lus kyi rtog pa sbyangs //
NK084(yu)001:1219: gser dpe' zhun lta bu'i bdag gi sems dag las //
NK084(yu)001:1221: thugs kar thim nas sku'i dbyig /rdo rje'i lam byung
NK084(yu)001:1222: yum gyi mkha' //yum gyi mkha' la bab pa dang
NK084(yu)001:1223: / h'u gi 'od kyis yum yang 'od du zhu /
NK084(yu)001:1224: chos sku byang chub sems su gnas //
NK084(yu)001:1225: snang la rang bzhin myed pa'i sku /
NK084(yu)001:1226: gsal la rtog pa myed pa'i thugs su gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:1227: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK084(yu)001:1228: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gzhan rnams kyang rang rang gi yi ge'i sgra tsam byung bas /
NK084(yu)001:1229: bzhi bzhi rtsa gnyis sgra byung bas //
NK084(yu)001:1230: sngags kyi sgras bskul nas gnas pa de /
NK084(yu)001:1231: byang chub sems su gcig par thim //
NK084(yu)001:1232: dbus kyi gtso' bo'i 'od phung la gcig par thim mo //
NK084(yu)001:1233: de nas snying po dran tsam gyis //
NK084(yu)001:1234: lha thams cad 'od du zhu nas 'od kyi gong bu cig tu gnas pa de la /
NK084(yu)001:1235: a dang k+sha dang gnyis kyi snying po dran tsam gyis /
NK084(yu)001:1236: a k+sha gsung gi phyag rgya gnyis //
NK084(yu)001:1237: 'od kyi gong bu de gsung gi yi ge a k+sha gnyis su gyur te /
NK084(yu)001:1238: de las sku bskyed pa'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' bas na phyag rgya gnyis zhes bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:1239: cho ga gsum gyi sbyor ba yis //
NK084(yu)001:1240: 'od kyi gong bu las a dang k+sha gnyis su gyur pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1242: des 'phro 'dus pa las rdo rje dang dril bur gyur pa ni thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho ga'o //
NK084(yu)001:1243: de 'phro 'dus pa las sku phra mor gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1244: phyag rgya chen po'i sku gnyis rdzogs //
NK084(yu)001:1245: sku phra mo 'phro 'dus pa las sngags brjod pas
NK084(yu)001:1246: dpal kun tu bzang po yab yum du gyur par
NK084(yu)001:1247: bsgom pa ni / sku mdog mthing ka zhal gcig phyag ga nyis pa /
NK084(yu)001:1249: phyag mnyam bzhag tu gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1250: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan par bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:1252: yab kyi gsang ba h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga
NK084(yu)001:1253: pa chu sbugs su yi ge gyis mtshan mar bskyed
NK084(yu)001:1254: do // h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga +amo /
NK084(yu)001:1255: yang na rtsa bar +amo sked par h'u rtse mor phata bsam par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:1256: pam las pad ma 'dab brgyad am //
NK084(yu)001:1257: yum gyi mkha' pam las pad ma 'dab brgyad du gyur pa'i dbus su nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK084(yu)001:1258: de'i steng du bsam par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:1259: kun tu bzang po'i dbu'i gnas lngar /
NK084(yu)001:1260: rin po che'i khang bu lnga'i nang du yi ge lnga bkod pas /
NK084(yu)001:1261: 'og min nas rigs lnga spyan drangs te /
NK084(yu)001:1262: mdun gyi nam ka la bzhugs pa de'i thabs dang
NK084(yu)001:1263: shes rab gnyis su myed pa de'i byang chub sems
NK084(yu)001:1264: dbu'i yi ge lnga la thim pa dang don ye
NK084(yu)001:1266: ma h+aa shu nya ta la sogs te'i sngags kyis nga rgyal bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:1267: de nas nam mkha'i rigs lnga dbu'i khang bu lnga'i
NK084(yu)001:1268: nang du spyan drangs la dbu' rgyan du bzhugs su
NK084(yu)001:1269: gsol lo // byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1270: lha rnams kyi spyi bo dang mgrin pa dang snying kar /
NK084(yu)001:1271: nyi ma dang zla ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1273: de'i steng du spyi bor mgrin par am thugs khar h'u bsam /
NK084(yu)001:1277: rdo rje sems dpar bskyed la /
NK084(yu)001:1279: barjesa su chags pas de bzhin bskul //
NK084(yu)001:1280: yum gyis yab la skul ba /
NK084(yu)001:1281: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis rjes su chags pa'i bdag nyid ma'am /
NK084(yu)001:1282: yul nga yi yin zhes ba bskul lo //
NK084(yu)001:1283: yab kyis yum la lan byin pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1284: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi mchod pa chen
NK084(yu)001:1285: po'i rdo rje'i rang bzhin nga'am bdag nyid yin zhes
NK084(yu)001:1287: +amo sarba thams cad ta de bzhin gshegs pa th+aa
NK084(yu)001:1288: ga ta ma chen po h+aa a nu rjes su
NK084(yu)001:1289: chags pa ra ga badz+ra rdo rje swa b+ha ba
NK084(yu)001:1290: ngo bo nyid ad bdag nyid ma ko nga'o ham
NK084(yu)001:1291: / +amo sarba thams cad ta de bzhin gshegs pa
NK084(yu)001:1292: th+aa ga ta ma h+aa chen po pu tsa mchod
NK084(yu)001:1293: pa badz+ra rdo rje swa b+ha ngo ba nyid ba
NK084(yu)001:1294: ad bdag nyid ma ko ham nga'o //
NK084(yu)001:1295: yum gyi pad mo'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK084(yu)001:1296: yum kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' pad ma 'dab brgyad
NK084(yu)001:1297: pa'i dal du ba ga bde stong gi nyams dang
NK084(yu)001:1298: ldan pa de / bde' ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK084(yu)001:1299: yab kun tu bzang po'i lhag pa byang chub kyi sems thugs yang dag pa'i bde' ba de /
NK084(yu)001:1300: yab kyis yum la dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rgyur spro ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1301: gzhal yas thig gdab snying po bkod //
NK084(yu)001:1302: yum gyi mkhar byang chub sems dang po spros pas dal du gyur /
NK084(yu)001:1303: gnyis pa spros pas thig gdab /
NK084(yu)001:1304: gsum pas dal yongs su rdzogs /
NK084(yu)001:1307: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gsal lo //
NK084(yu)001:1308: de las spro dang bsdu ba yis //
NK084(yu)001:1309: de nas 'phros pas snying po ka kha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1310: thugs kyi phyag rgya bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK084(yu)001:1312: thugs mtshan bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1314: de las yang phar 'phros tshur 'dus pa las sku phra mo bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1315: so so'i sngags kyis skyed cing gdon //
NK084(yu)001:1316: de nas yum gyi mkha'i nang na gnas pa'i sku
NK084(yu)001:1317: phra mo de rang rang gi sngags brjod pas phyi
NK084(yu)001:1319: dbus su h'u badz+ra 'drig /gtso' bo yab yum gyi sngags bstan /
NK084(yu)001:1320: zhes brjod pas dbus su bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK084(yu)001:1322: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing ka'i zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1323: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas /
NK084(yu)001:1324: dril bu pad ma ral gri g.yon na snams pa /
NK084(yu)001:1325: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK084(yu)001:1326: zhabs rdzogs pa'i skyil dkrung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1327: shar du +amo dzi na 'dzig /ces pas shar du rnam par snang mdzad /
NK084(yu)001:1328: zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas dmar g.yon sngo dbus dkar zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1329: 'khor lo rin chen rdo rje g.yas /
NK084(yu)001:1330: dril bu pad ma ral gri g.yon /
NK084(yu)001:1331: zhabs rdzogs pa'i skyil dkrung du bzhugs so //
NK084(yu)001:1332: lhor s+w+aa rad na 'drig /ces pas lhor rin chen 'byung ldan zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK084(yu)001:1333: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1334: rin chen 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas /
NK084(yu)001:1335: dril bu pad ma ral gri g.yon na snams so //
NK084(yu)001:1336: nub tu +amo a ro lig ces pas nub tu snang ba mtha' yas zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK084(yu)001:1337: g.yas sngo g.yon dkar dbus dmar zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1338: pad ma 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas /
NK084(yu)001:1339: dril bu rin chen ral gri g.yon na snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1340: byang du ha prad nya 'drig /ces pas byang du don yod grub pa zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK084(yu)001:1341: g.yos dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1342: ral gri 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas dril bu pad ma rin chen /
NK084(yu)001:1343: dbus mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK084(yu)001:1344: dbyings phyug ma mthing ka g.yas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK084(yu)001:1348: sangs rgyas spyan dkar mo g.yas yab la 'khyud pa g.yon dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1351: ma ma ki ser mo g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa g.yon pa dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1354: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa /
NK084(yu)001:1355: g.yon pa dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1358: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang khu g.yas pa yab ya 'khyud pa /
NK084(yu)001:1363: sa'i snying po g.yas rin chen myu gu /
NK084(yu)001:1365: tram a ka ra rba ya /
NK084(yu)001:1367: nam mkha'i snying po ser po g.yas ral gri g.yon dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1368: hri pad ma ban d+ha ya /
NK084(yu)001:1370: spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad ma dkar po g.yon dril bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:1371: dzim ku ru pa na hri /
NK084(yu)001:1373: phyag na rdo rje ljang khu g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1374: h'u la se sa ma ya stam /
NK084(yu)001:1375: la se sgeg mo dkar mo g.yas me long thogs pa /
NK084(yu)001:1376: g.yon 'ging bag gi tshul can sems pa sa snying gi yum 'khril sbyor du gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:1377: tram ma le sa ma ya ho /
NK084(yu)001:1378: ma le ma ser mo 'phreng ba spyi bor 'dren
NK084(yu)001:1379: pa nam mkha' snying po dang 'khril sbyor du gnas
NK084(yu)001:1380: so // hri g+hir ti ra go ya ham /
NK084(yu)001:1381: dbyangs ma dmar mo pi wang sbreng ba spyan ras gzigs kyi yum mo //
NK084(yu)001:1382: a ni ra ti ra go ya mi /
NK084(yu)001:1383: gar ma ljang khu phyag rgya gar sgyur ma phyag na rdo rje yum mo //
NK084(yu)001:1384: phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum bstan /
NK084(yu)001:1385: me d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK084(yu)001:1386: byams pa dkar po klu shing g.yas /
NK084(yu)001:1389: th+l+him swa ra ba ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK084(yu)001:1390: lho nub tu sgrib sel ser po chos kyi 'khor lo dang dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1391: h'u swa ra rtsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK084(yu)001:1392: nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang dmar po g.yas rin chen snye ma g.yon dril bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:1393: mum sh+ri a ram ga s+w+aa h+aa /
NK084(yu)001:1394: byang shar gru chad la 'jam dpal ljang khu g.yas ud dpal /
NK084(yu)001:1396: dza du pa pra be sha /du pe ma dkar
NK084(yu)001:1397: mo spos phor thogs pa byams pa'i yum yin no
NK084(yu)001:1398: // h'u pus pa a be sha /push+pe ma ser
NK084(yu)001:1399: mo me tog thogs pa sgrib sel gyi yum mo
NK084(yu)001:1400: // // bam di pa su ki ni /
NK084(yu)001:1401: a lo ke dmar mo mar me thogs pa sgrib sel gyi yum mo //
NK084(yu)001:1402: ho g+han d+he tsi ta ho //
NK084(yu)001:1403: g+han d+he ma ljang khu dri chab thogs pa 'jam dpal gyi yum mo //
NK084(yu)001:1404: sgo ba yab yum gyi sngags /
NK084(yu)001:1405: h'u ya man ta krid phata /
NK084(yu)001:1406: shar sgor gshin rje gshed zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK084(yu)001:1407: g.yas ljang g.yon sngon dbus dkar zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1408: dang po gnyis mi 'go mnan pa /
NK084(yu)001:1411: h'u big nan ta krid phata /
NK084(yu)001:1412: lhor stobs po che zhal gsum phyag drug pa g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus sngo zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1413: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis rdo rje gnon pa /
NK084(yu)001:1416: h'u pad ma ta krid phata /
NK084(yu)001:1417: nub tu rta mgrin zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK084(yu)001:1418: g.yas sngo g.yon dkar dbus dmar zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1419: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis thod pa sbrul gyis rgyan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1420: g.yas pad ma rdo rje g.yon ral gri sdig 'jug go //
NK084(yu)001:1421: h'u prad nya ta krid phata /
NK084(yu)001:1422: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba g.yas dmar g.yon dkar dbus ljang zhal /
NK084(yu)001:1423: g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis rdo rje rgya gram /
NK084(yu)001:1424: g.yas gnyis na ral gri rdo rje /
NK084(yu)001:1426: +amo badz+ra ma h+aa d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK084(yu)001:1427: shar du gshin rje gshed po'i yum lcags kyu ma'i sngags so //
NK084(yu)001:1428: +amo ma h+aa rad na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK084(yu)001:1429: lhor stobs po che'i yum ser mo zhags pa ma'i sngags so //
NK084(yu)001:1430: +amo ma h+aa pad ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK084(yu)001:1431: nub tu rta mgrin gyi yum dmar mo lcags sgrog ma'i sngags so //
NK084(yu)001:1432: +amo ma h+aa ka ra ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK084(yu)001:1433: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i yum ljang khu dril bu ma'i sngags so //
NK084(yu)001:1434: kun bzang yab yum gyi sngags bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1435: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsita h'u /
NK084(yu)001:1436: dkyil 'khor shar gyi bar khyams su kun tu bzang
NK084(yu)001:1437: po mthing ka skyil dkrung mnyam bzhag can du gnas
NK084(yu)001:1438: so // a a a badz+ra pa tra sa ma ya +amo /
NK084(yu)001:1439: dkyil 'khor nub kyi bar khyams su kun bzang mo mthing sngon mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can no //
NK084(yu)001:1440: thub pa drug gi sngags bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1442: byang shar mtshams su lha'i thub pa ser po pi wang thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1443: +amo mu ne h'u krum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK084(yu)001:1444: shar lho mtshams su lha ma yin gyi thub pa ser po go cha thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1446: lho na mi'i thub pa ser po sreg shang dang par bu thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1447: thub drug spyi'i ni ser po /
NK084(yu)001:1448: sgo sgor gang la gang 'dul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1450: lho nub byol song gi thub pa ser po po ti thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1452: nub byang du yi dwags kyi thub pa ser po rad na'i sgrom bu thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1454: byang du dmyal ba'i thub pa ser po me chu thogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1455: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK084(yu)001:1457: rgyal ba rigs lnga la gdan lnga rtsegs nyi shu rtsa lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:1458: sems dpa' sems ma la nyi zla pad ma sum rtsegs so //
NK084(yu)001:1459: thub pa la pad ma rkyang pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1460: kun bzang yab yum la nyi zla pad ma'o //
NK084(yu)001:1461: sgo ba la rdo rje brag gi steng na nyi ma rkyang pas so //
NK084(yu)001:1462: rdzogs dang zhes pas rigs lnga rdzogs pa'i skyil dkrung zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:1463: rdo rje'i skyil dkrung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1465: sems dpa' rnams mdzad pa ma rdzogs pas phyed skyil la /
NK084(yu)001:1469: sgo ba gyad kyi dor thabs so //
NK084(yu)001:1470: yum rnams pad ma'i skyil dkrung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:1471: kun tu bzang po mnyam pa'i skyil dkrung /
NK084(yu)001:1472: kun tu bzang mo pad ma'i skyil dkrung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:1473: 'khor lor rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK084(yu)001:1475: rgyal po ni rigs lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:1476: rnam shes las rgyal ba rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK084(yu)001:1477: gzugs kyi phung po las rgyal ba rnam snang /
NK084(yu)001:1478: tshor ba las rgyal ba rin 'byung /
NK084(yu)001:1479: 'du shes las rgyal ba snang mtha' /
NK084(yu)001:1480: 'du byed las rgyal ba don yod grub pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1481: rgyal mo ni yum lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:1482: nam ka las rgyal ba dbyings phyug ma /
NK084(yu)001:1486: rlung las rgyal ba dam tshig sgrol ma /
NK084(yu)001:1487: de rnams dbus na 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi' /
NK084(yu)001:1488: lte ba dang lnga la bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1490: g.yas nas mthong thos snom pa dang //
NK084(yu)001:1491: rdo rje sems dpa'i g.yas kyi rtsibs 'chan la /
NK084(yu)001:1492: mthong ba dmyig gi rnam par shes pa sa'i snying po dang /
NK084(yu)001:1493: thos pa rna ba'i rnam par shes pa phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK084(yu)001:1494: snam pa sna'i rnam par shes pa spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK084(yu)001:1495: myong ba lce'i rnam par shes pa nam mkha'i snying po'o //
NK084(yu)001:1496: 'khor lo'i rtsibs 'chan bzhi la bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1497: nang gi sems dpa' zhes bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1498: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK084(yu)001:1499: spyad par bya ba'i phyir na btsun mo ste /
NK084(yu)001:1500: dmyig gis gzugs la spyod pas na btsun mo'o //
NK084(yu)001:1501: de yang sa'i snying po'i yum la se ma'o //
NK084(yu)001:1502: de bzhin du ma le ma dang /
NK084(yu)001:1505: spyad bya'i yul du gyur pas na btsun mo /
NK084(yu)001:1506: gnyis su myed par 'khril ba'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NK084(yu)001:1508: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang //
NK084(yu)001:1509: thos byed snom byed myong byed rnams //
NK084(yu)001:1510: gru chad la ni phyi'i sems dpa' bzhugs pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1511: dmyig gi dbang po ni mthong byed la /
NK084(yu)001:1512: de gnas 'gyur ba ni byams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1513: de bzhin du thos byed rna ba'i dbang po sgrib sel /
NK084(yu)001:1514: snom byed sna'i dbang po kun bzang /
NK084(yu)001:1515: myong byed lce'i dbang po 'jam dpa' rnams ni gru chad bzhi la bzhugs so //
NK084(yu)001:1516: de bas bzhi po de rnams zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:1517: de dbang po'i phyi na yod pas phyi'i sems dpa' zhes kyang bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:1518: don du na lha la phyi nang myed de /
NK084(yu)001:1519: sems can gyi rtog tshogs la dgongs pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1520: sems dpa' la yang phyi nang gnyis so //
NK084(yu)001:1521: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK084(yu)001:1522: spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pas na btsun mo ste /
NK084(yu)001:1527: dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhi la dbang bas na /
NK084(yu)001:1532: bar khyams la ni thub drug dang //
NK084(yu)001:1534: byang shar du lha'i thub pa /
NK084(yu)001:1535: shar lhor lha ma yin gyi thub pa /
NK084(yu)001:1537: lho nub tu byol song gi thub pa /
NK084(yu)001:1538: nub byang du yi dwags kyi thub pa /
NK084(yu)001:1539: byang du dmyal ba'i thub pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1540: mdun dang rgyab tu byed pa dang //
NK084(yu)001:1541: bya ba dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK084(yu)001:1543: bar khyams kyi shar nub gnyis su kun bzang yab yum gnyis bzhugs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1544: rdo rje sems dpa'i mdun ngos su byed pa po kun tu bzang po gnas te /
NK084(yu)001:1545: yid kyi rnam par shes pa gnas 'gyur ba yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1546: sems can gyi dus na byed pa po thams cad yid /
NK084(yu)001:1547: sangs rgyas kyi dus na rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi
NK084(yu)001:1548: byed pa po thams cad kun tu bzang po yin
NK084(yu)001:1549: no // rdo rje sems dpa'i rgyab ngos na bya ba mo kun tu bzang mo gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1550: de yang sems can gyi dus na bya ba'i gzhir gyur pa kun gazhi'o //
NK084(yu)001:1551: sangs rgyas dus na yang chos kyi dbyings so //
NK084(yu)001:1552: des yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po dang /
NK084(yu)001:1553: chos bya ba mo kun tu bzang po gnyis /
NK084(yu)001:1554: yid kyi spyad bya kun gzhi yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1555: kun bzang yab yum gnyis so //
NK084(yu)001:1556: sgo khyud bzhi la 'joms pa ni //
NK084(yu)001:1557: sgo ba yab yum brgyad bstan /
NK084(yu)001:1558: sgo khyud bzhi la zhes pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1559: g.yas g.yon gyi sgo khyud la sgo ba bzhi gnas pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1561: reg pa'i rtog pa 'joms pa gshin rje gshed reg bya stobs po che /
NK084(yu)001:1563: reg shes kyi rtog pa 'joms pa bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1564: khro bo'i tshul du gnas pas na 'joms pa'o zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:1565: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK084(yu)001:1566: btsun mo ni spyad bya'i yul du gyur pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1567: lus kyi dbang po bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:1568: rtag pa dang chad pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1569: bdag dang mtshan ma bzhi la dbang bas na bzhi po de gnas su dag pas ni /
NK084(yu)001:1574: de bas na dbang po lnga'i las byed lta bu ni lus kyi dbang po yin la /
