NK084(yu)001:1575: lha'i las byed pa yin pas na chos mthun pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1576: zhi ba'i lha 'bu ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis zhes bzhed pa yin pa la /
NK084(yu)001:1577: khro bo yab yum brgyad yod pas /
NK084(yu)001:1578: khro bo rnams zhi ba'i lhar 'agro'am mi 'gro zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:1579: spyir rnal 'byor pas grub par bya ba'i zhi ba'i
NK084(yu)001:1580: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK084(yu)001:1581: rgyud zhi bas na zhi ba zer la /
NK084(yu)001:1584: khro rtags drug cu rtsa brgyad dang ldan pas khro bo zer ro //
NK084(yu)001:1585: 'o na sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud zhi na sgo ba la khro bo'i ming myed zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:1587: zhi ba las ltos na khro bo yin yang /
NK084(yu)001:1588: khro bo'i gar dgu' dang khro rtags myed de /
NK084(yu)001:1589: sku khro tshul dang bcas par snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1591: de bas na cung zad khro bo lha brgyad zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:1592: stag dang sbrul gyi rgyan tsam ma bkag go //
NK084(yu)001:1593: dngos su sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud zhi bar gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:1594: de bas na khro bo mi zer te 'joms pa zhes bshad do //
NK084(yu)001:1596: yab rnams kyi g.yon dang po na snams so //
NK084(yu)001:1597: rdo rje mi bskyod pa 'khor lo rnam snang gi rin po che //
NK084(yu)001:1598: rin 'byung gi rigs lnga spyi'i phyag mtshan /
NK084(yu)001:1599: pad ma snang mtha'i ral gri don grub kyi dril bu 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:1600: spyir gnas 'phrog rtsis na zhal gsum phyag drug tu byed pa ni gong bzhin no //
NK084(yu)001:1601: 'di g.yas g.yon gyi dang po rnams bshad pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1602: mi bskyod pa'i g.yas dang po na rdo rje 'dzin pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1603: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1604: rnam par snang mdzad kyi g.yas dang po na 'khor lo snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1605: nyon mongs pa thams cad gcod pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1606: rin 'byung gi g.yas dang po na rin po che
NK084(yu)001:1607: 'dzin pa ni dgos 'dod re ba thams cad skong
NK084(yu)001:1608: ba'o // snang ba mtha' yas kyi g.yas dang po na pad ma snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1609: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1610: don yod grub pa'i g.yas dang po na ral gri snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1611: rtog pa thams cad rtsad nas gcod cing /
NK084(yu)001:1612: mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang ldan pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1613: g.yon gyi phyag na dril bu snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1614: shes rab spros pa myed pas chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1615: bar ma dang tha ma rnams ni de dag las
NK084(yu)001:1616: gong 'og tu sgyur te gnas 'phrog rtsis nas byed
NK084(yu)001:1617: pa'o // dril bu yum rnams kyi g.yon na 'dzin no //
NK084(yu)001:1618: g.yas pa rnams rang rang gi yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1619: ud dpal byang shar mtshams kyi gru chad la 'jam
NK084(yu)001:1620: dpal gyi klu shing la sogs shar lho mtshams gru
NK084(yu)001:1622: rin chen myu gu shar lho mtshams kyi rtsibs mchan
NK084(yu)001:1623: la sa'i snying po ral gri lho nub mtshams kyi
NK084(yu)001:1624: rtsibs mchan la nam ka snying po 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:1625: pad ma dkar po nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la
NK084(yu)001:1626: spyan ras gzigs rdo rje byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan
NK084(yu)001:1628: chos kyi 'khor lo lho nub gru chad la sgrib
NK084(yu)001:1629: sel gyi rin chen nub byang gru chad la kun
NK084(yu)001:1631: 'dir sems dpa' rnams kyi phyag mtshan gyi skabs su /
NK084(yu)001:1632: gzhung 'khrugs pa sdeb ste bshad na /
NK084(yu)001:1633: rnam par shes pa'i sems dpa' spyi'i phyag mtshan ni /
NK084(yu)001:1634: sa'i snying po rin po che'i myu gu 'dzin pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1635: dgos 'dod zad pa myed pa 'byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1636: nam mkha'i snying po ral gri 'dzin pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1637: nyon mongs pa thams cad gcod pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1638: spyan ras gzigs pad ma dkar po snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1639: nyon mongs pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1640: phyag na rdo rje snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1641: ye shes lnga yis nyon mongs pa 'joms pa'i stobs dang ldan pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1642: de rnams ni nang gi sems dpa' bzhi'o //
NK084(yu)001:1644: byams pa'i phyag na klu shing gi me tog snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1645: nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba thams cad zil gyis ma non pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1646: sgrib pa rnam par sel ba chos kyi 'khor lo snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1647: rtog pa'i dras thag thams cad gcod pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1648: kun tu bzang po rin po che'i snye ma snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1649: sems can thams cad la dgos 'dod re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1650: 'jam dpal ud dpal snams pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1651: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid thams cad la 'gag pa myed par mkhyen cing /
NK084(yu)001:1652: nyes pa'i skyon dang bral ba'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1654: g.yon rnams na dril bu snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1656: phyag mtshan de dag yang snang la rang bzhin myed pa /
NK084(yu)001:1657: gsal la rtog pa myed pa /
NK084(yu)001:1660: gzugs mdzes la se ma rin chen 'phreng ba ma le ma dang //
NK084(yu)001:1662: pi wang g+hirti gar mkhan ni rti mchog nyid de //
NK084(yu)001:1663: lha mo la se ma gzugs mdzes me long snams nas 'gying bag tu bzhugs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1664: sa'i snying po dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde' bas dgyes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1665: ma le ma 'phreng ba thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1666: nam mkha'i snying po dang bde' ba rgyun mi chad pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1667: g+hir ti ma pi wang thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1668: spyan ras gzigs dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde' ba'i sgra sgrogs pa'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1669: nir ti ma gar sgyur ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:1670: phyag na rdo rje dang gnyis su myed pa'i ye shes la dbang sgyur ba'i rtags so //
NK084(yu)001:1671: nang gi sems ma yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1672: nang gi mchod rdzas phyag na snams pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1673: me tog pu sh+pe 'phreng dang spos mchog d+hu sh+pe ma //
NK084(yu)001:1674: mar me a lo ke byug pa g+han d+he la sogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:1675: d+hush+pe ma spos thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1676: byams pa dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde ba'i 'od zer 'phros pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1677: pu sh+pe ma me tog thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1678: sgrib pa rnam par sel ba dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde ba'i mtshan par byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1679: a lo ke mar me thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1680: kun tu bzang po dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde' ba gsal ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1681: gan d+he ma dri chab thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1682: 'jam dpal dang gnyis su myed pa'i bde' bas gsil bar byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1683: des na phyi'i sems ma yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:1684: phyi'i mchod snams pa'i tshul lo //
NK084(yu)001:1685: las yab la 'khril yum zhing chos yum la yab zhal bstan //
NK084(yu)001:1686: yum rnams yab kyi sku la 'khril zhing /
NK084(yu)001:1687: yab rnams yum chos kyi rang bzhin la zhal bstan nas /
NK084(yu)001:1688: gcig la gcig 'dud pa'i tshul lo //
NK084(yu)001:1689: dbu' yab kyi rnams 'byo ya zhal zhing 'dud yum gyi dbu' rnams ma zhal pa'i tshul //
NK084(yu)001:1690: gong gi phyag rgya chen po las la 'khril zhing chos la bstan pa'i skabs kyi bzhin //
NK084(yu)001:1691: gnyis yab yum myed chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril lo //
NK084(yu)001:1692: lha mo de dag ni yab re re dang yum
NK084(yu)001:1693: re re thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed par
NK084(yu)001:1694: sbyor ba re re la yang rang bzhin gyis tshang
NK084(yu)001:1695: bar bya'o // de ltar sems dpa' dang sems ma yab yum de dag kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1696: yum rnams yab kyi sku la gnyis su myed par 'khril ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1697: yab yum gnyis gcig la gcig bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:1700: dbyings dang ye shes tha mi dad par snyoms par 'jug pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1701: sgo bzhi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK084(yu)001:1702: sgo ba bzhi'i phyag rgya bstan /
NK084(yu)001:1703: n+rir shar du gshin rje'i mgo' bsdengs dang rdo rje lhor stobs po che'i non //
NK084(yu)001:1704: thod sprul chen nub tu rta mgrin gyi po mnon pa dang //
NK084(yu)001:1705: rdo rje rgya gram las byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i kyis mnon //
NK084(yu)001:1706: gshin rje gshed mi 'go'i dbyug pa thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1707: nyon mongs pa dang bgegs dang log rtogs shing 'joms pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1708: stobs po che rdo rjes sa gnon pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1709: nyon mongs pa dang bgegs thams cad ldang mi nus pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1710: rta mgrin thod pa sbrul gyis rgyan pa thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1711: bgegs kyis zhe sdang gnas su dag nas chos kyi dbyings su mkhyen pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1712: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1713: 'phrin las rnam bzhis thams cad kyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1714: de bas na phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis na de ltar gnas la /
NK084(yu)001:1715: gzhan ma zhal gsum phyag drug tu byed na gong du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK084(yu)001:1716: lcags kyu shar gyi sgo ma'i zhags pa nub kyi lcags sgrog spo ta byang gi dril bu ho //
NK084(yu)001:1717: lha mo lcags kyu ma ni /
NK084(yu)001:1718: thugs rjes sems can mya ngan las 'das su 'dren pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1720: sems can thugs rjes drangs nas 'khor bar mi gtong ba'i rda'o //
NK084(yu)001:1721: lcags sgrog ma ni sems can de dag bde' bar
NK084(yu)001:1722: gshegs pa'i thugs ye shes dbyer med pa'i sa la
NK084(yu)001:1723: 'god pa'o // dril bu ma ni sems can de dag phyir ldog pa'i sa la bkod nas /
NK084(yu)001:1724: bde ba chen pos mnyes pa dang tshim par byed pa'i brdar ba stan no //
NK084(yu)001:1725: sgo bzhir khro bo yab yum gnas pa de dag kyang //
NK084(yu)001:1726: 'dud yum tshul yab 'khril ba gong ma sems dpa' bzhin no //
NK084(yu)001:1727: khro bo yab yum de dag kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1728: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1729: yab kyis yum la 'dud pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1730: yum yab kyi sku la gnyis su myed par 'khril ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1731: de yang gong du bstan pa'i rigs lnga sems dpa' dang 'dra'o //
NK084(yu)001:1732: yab yum gnyis su myed pa sgo bzhir gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1733: thub lus ngag yid drug grangs phyag rgya sna tshogs ma nges te //
NK084(yu)001:1735: mdor bsdus bsgom bde' bas na phyag rgya drug tu bstan //
NK084(yu)001:1736: thub pa ni sku gsung thugs thub pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1737: de yang sku thub pa rtag dang bya byed spangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1738: gsung thub pa ni ngag mi dga' ba bzhi spangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1739: thugs thub pa ni yid kyi mi dge' ba gsum spangs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1740: de dag ni gdul bya gang la gang ltar mos pa bzhin du don mdzad pas /
NK084(yu)001:1741: phyir phyag rgya ma nges pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1742: de yang dal du bsgom pa'i dus su /
NK084(yu)001:1743: ting nge 'dzin gyi dmigs pa gsal ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:1744: mdo' drug ba sdus nas bstan pa ni sreg par logs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1745: thub pa drug gi yab yum la /
NK084(yu)001:1746: don gyi yum dang rtags kyi yum gnyis las /
NK084(yu)001:1747: sprul pa'i sku de dag ni /
NK084(yu)001:1748: grogs mi bde' ba spong zhing /
NK084(yu)001:1750: rtags kyi yum ni ma ba stan no //
NK084(yu)001:1751: don gyi yum ni chos kyi dbyings dang dus thams cad du 'du 'bral myed par bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1752: bsreg mi'i thub pa'i phyag mtshan dpar dang ni pi lha'i thub pa'i wang dang //
NK084(yu)001:1753: go cha lha ma yin gyi thub pa'i po ti
NK084(yu)001:1754: byol song gi thub pa'i rin chen yi dwags thub
NK084(yu)001:1755: pa'i sgrom // me dang dmyal ba'i thub pa chu ni rab tu bstan //
NK084(yu)001:1756: yum rtags kyi yum ni dmigs dngos su myed chos de don gyi yum kyi dbyings //
NK084(yu)001:1757: lha'i thub pa'i pi wang thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1758: lha rol mo la dga' ba de dag la /
NK084(yu)001:1759: 'dul byed kyi gdul bya dang 'thun par 'dul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1760: de yang de dag gi le lo dang g.yeng ba las bzlog nas /
NK084(yu)001:1761: bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1762: lha ma yin gyi thub pa go cha thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1763: de dag 'thun par bstan pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1765: brtson 'grus kyi pha rol du phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1766: mi'i thub pa sreg shang dang par bu thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1768: tshul khrims kyi pha rol du phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1769: byol song gi thub pa po ti thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1770: gti' mug gi mun pa de dag par mdzad nas /
NK084(yu)001:1771: shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1772: yi dwags kyi thub pa rin po che'i sgrom bu thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1773: ser sna'i 'dud pa las blo zlog nas /
NK084(yu)001:1774: sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1775: dmyal ba'i thub pa me chu thogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1776: zhe sdang gi ngo bo las blo zlog nas /
NK084(yu)001:1777: bzod pa'i pha rol du phyin pa la 'god par mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:1778: kun bzang mtshan mnyam bzhag phyag rgya ye shes phyag mtshan 'phro //
NK084(yu)001:1780: yum yum 'gyur mnyam phyag rgya rdzogs pad mo'i zhabs dkyil //
NK084(yu)001:1781: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs ma nges pa te //
NK084(yu)001:1782: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa nyid //
NK084(yu)001:1783: yang na rdo rje thal mo nyid //
NK084(yu)001:1784: kun tu bzang po ni zhabs brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo krung du bzhugs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1785: phyag mnyam bzhag tu gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1786: mnyam bzhag steng na phyag sor la ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1787: de'i yum du gyur pa ni kun tu bzang mo ste /
NK084(yu)001:1788: zhabs pad ma'i dkyil krung zhabs mthil gnyis sprad nas bzhugs pa /
NK084(yu)001:1789: phyag mnyam par bzhag pa las mdzub mo gnyis rtse sprad nas bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1790: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs gnas te /
NK084(yu)001:1792: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa rnam snang gi phyag rgya'am /
NK084(yu)001:1793: yang na rdo rje thal mo'i phyag rgya'i bcing ngo //
NK084(yu)001:1794: mthing ka rdo rje'i rigs dkar po de bzhin rigs ser rin chen rigs le'u brgan pad ma'i rigs /
NK084(yu)001:1795: ljang khu las kyi rigs la sogs so so lha grangs dang sbyar ba'o sna tshogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:1796: spyir sku mdog la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:1797: rang bzhin gyi sku mdog dang /
NK084(yu)001:1799: de la rang bzhin gyi sku mdog ni /
NK084(yu)001:1804: de yang nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa dung lta bu dang /
NK084(yu)001:1805: snum la 'dril ba me tog ku mu ta lta bu dang /
NK084(yu)001:1806: gsal ba nyi ma lta bu /
NK084(yu)001:1807: dang zhing gsal ba zla ba lta bu /
NK084(yu)001:1808: mtsher ba gangs la nyi ma shar ba lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:1809: de rnams ni spyir khyab la /
NK084(yu)001:1814: mthing ka don chos kyi dbyings la nyon mongs pas ma slad pas mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1815: de yang kun tu bzang po yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1816: mi bskyod pa yab yum sku mdog mthing kar bzhugs so //
NK084(yu)001:1817: de ni rdo rje rigs kyi sku mdog go //
NK084(yu)001:1819: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:1821: sa'i snying po yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1823: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK084(yu)001:1824: ser po ni che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags te /
NK084(yu)001:1825: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1826: nam mkha'i snying po yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1827: mi'i thub pa'i sku mdog ste /
NK084(yu)001:1828: de ni rin po che'i rigs so //
NK084(yu)001:1829: dmar po ni thugs rje'i 'gro ba'i don la chags pa'i rtags te /
NK084(yu)001:1830: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1831: spyan ras gzigs yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1832: yi dwags kyi thub pa'i sku mdog ste /
NK084(yu)001:1833: de ni pad ma'i rigs so //
NK084(yu)001:1834: ljang khu ni 'phrin las bzhis 'gro ba thams cad kyi don mdzad pa'i rtags te /
NK084(yu)001:1835: don yod grub pa yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1837: dmyal ba'i thub pa'i sku mdog ste /
NK084(yu)001:1838: de ni las kyi rigs so //
NK084(yu)001:1840: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga'am yang na mthing ka rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum /
NK084(yu)001:1841: nam mkha'i snying po yab yum /
NK084(yu)001:1844: dkar po ni rnam snang yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:1846: ser po ni rin 'byung dang thub pa drug go //
NK084(yu)001:1847: dmar po ni snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK084(yu)001:1850: ljang khu ni don yod grub pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1853: sgo ba bzhi phyogs mthun no //
NK084(yu)001:1854: sna tshogs pa ni rang rang ma 'dres pa gsal lo //
NK084(yu)001:1857: gnyen zhe sdang dag pas lcug khong khro dag pas
NK084(yu)001:1858: 'khril 'dod chags dag pas ldem nga rgyal dag pas
NK084(yu)001:1859: gzhon tshul gti' mug dag pas can //
NK084(yu)001:1863: gsal 'phrag dog dag pas mtsher ser sna dag pas
NK084(yu)001:1864: lhun gdug bdag 'dzin dag pas gzi' brjid zhen pa
NK084(yu)001:1865: dag pas ldan // de la zhi ba'i tshul dgu' ni /
NK084(yu)001:1866: gnyen pa ni rin po che gser lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1867: gyong bo dang khengs pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1869: 'bras sa lu'i ljang pa lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1870: de yang rengs pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1871: 'khril ba ni dper na sbrul lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1872: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1873: so sor bzhugs pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1876: skyog po dang yon po lta bu ni spangs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1878: byis pa lo brgyad lon pa lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1880: rgan po khogs po lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1882: tshes bco' lnga'i zla ba lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1883: mog mog po'am nag nag po ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1885: nyi ma'i snying po lta bu ste /
NK084(yu)001:1886: phyogs gcig pa'am mi gcig pa lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1889: stur stur po ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1890: gzi' brjid dang ldan pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:1893: nor bu 'ching bu lta bu ni ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:1894: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku ni de ltar bas chog mi shes par bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1897: de yang sku'i ba spu'i bu ga gcig nas yang
NK084(yu)001:1898: 'od zer bye ba phrag khrig brgya stong drug cu
NK084(yu)001:1900: zhal gyi mdzod spu nas 'od zer kha dog mi
NK084(yu)001:1901: 'dra ba nyi shu rtsa lnga'i tshogs su 'phro ba'o
NK084(yu)001:1902: // de nyid gnas 'gyur bas khro bo'i dus kyi me dpung /
NK084(yu)001:1905: sgo bzhin gnas pa'i khro bo bzhi las kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1906: nyon mongs pa bsreg pa'i me dpung skal pa 'jig
NK084(yu)001:1907: pa'i dus kyi me lta bu ye shes kyi me
NK084(yu)001:1909: de yang ye shes kyi me yin pas na me
NK084(yu)001:1910: lce 'phreng ba ltar rgyus nas me dpung du 'khril
NK084(yu)001:1911: zhing 'bar ba'o // mtha' dbus myed par khyab pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:1912: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK084(yu)001:1913: phyi rol na yang ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:1914: de yang nam mkha' gar khyab pa chos dbyings kyis khyab la /
NK084(yu)001:1915: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par chos kyi dbyings
NK084(yu)001:1916: kyi ye shes rtogs pa'i rtags su lha'i gzhal yas
NK084(yu)001:1918: de bas na rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1919: mo ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ata ma ko & ham /
NK084(yu)001:1920: bdag gi spyi bor rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1921: nyi ma'i steng du rnam par snang mdzad /
NK084(yu)001:1922: sku mtshon gang ba gcig la sku mdog dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1923: ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1924: bdag gi dpral ba dngos su rin po che'i khang bu'i nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1925: nyi zla pad ma'i steng du /
NK084(yu)001:1926: rdo rje sems dpa'i mthing ga sa gnon gyi phyag rgya can bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1927: ma h+aa sa man ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1928: bdag gi ldan pa g.yas su rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1929: nyi zla pad ma'i steng du /
NK084(yu)001:1930: rin 'byung ser po sbyin gtong gi phyag rgya can bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1931: ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1932: bdag gi ltag khung du rin po che'i khang bu'i nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1933: nyi zla pad ma'i gdan stengs su snang ba mtha'
NK084(yu)001:1934: yas dmar po mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can bsam
NK084(yu)001:1935: mo // ma h+aa kri ta a nu ta dz+ny+aa na swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1936: bdag gi ldan pa g.yon du rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1937: nyi zla pad ma'i gdan stengs su /
NK084(yu)001:1938: don yod grub pa skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1939: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1940: bdag gi klad pa'i dung khang du 'khor lo rtsibs
NK084(yu)001:1941: brgyad kyi steng du rnam par snang mdzad du bsam
NK084(yu)001:1942: mo // sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1943: bdag gi lce stengs su pad ma 'dab brgyad kyi stengs su snang ba mtha' yas bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1944: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK084(yu)001:1945: bdag gi thugs kyi dpal be'u zur brgyad stengs su rdo rje sems dpa' bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1946: bdag gi spyi bo la sogs pa'i gnas lngar /
NK084(yu)001:1947: rin po che'i khang bu lnga'i nang du /
NK084(yu)001:1948: +aah h'u s+w+aa h+aa lnga las rigs lnga bsam /
NK084(yu)001:1949: sku gsung thugs kyi lhar bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1950: de nas yab yum sbyor ba byas pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas /
NK084(yu)001:1952: 'og min nas rigs lnga mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs nas /
NK084(yu)001:1953: yab yum sbyor ba byas pa'i byang sems las rig
NK084(yu)001:1954: pa'i lha mo bum pa thogs pa mang pos bdag
NK084(yu)001:1957: dbang rtags su rigs lnga'i dbu' rgyan bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1958: bde' bar gshegs pa'i rigs lngas ye shes lnga'i dbang skur /
NK084(yu)001:1959: sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlabs bsdus /
NK084(yu)001:1960: lha tshogs thams cad 'od du gsal bar gyur pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1961: de la lha re re la dbu' rgyan lnga bsam ste /
NK084(yu)001:1962: rang rang gi rigs kyis gtso' bo byas pa lnga lnga bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:1963: thub pa drug la mi byed de /
NK084(yu)001:1966: thub drug sprul pa'i skur gnas pas /
NK084(yu)001:1967: byin brlabs ur rgyan ma gsungs so //
NK084(yu)001:1969: 'dod pa'i yon tan spangs pa'i tshul yin pas /
NK084(yu)001:1970: chags lam gyi dbang mi bzhed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1971: sprul sku'i tshul du bzhugs pas /
NK084(yu)001:1972: dbu' rgyan mi bzhed pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:1973: sku gsung thugs dang ye shes lnga //
NK084(yu)001:1975: dbang dang ye shes lnga byin brlabs sku gsung thugs kun bsdus thim //
NK084(yu)001:1978: sa la sogs la phyag rgyar byas //
NK084(yu)001:1980: rnam grol rim pa thob 'gyur na //
NK084(yu)001:1982: sa la sku gdung gtab pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1984: ras sam dar la ris su bris pa'am /
NK084(yu)001:1986: rdo'am shing la 'bur du skos pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1987: gser dngul zangs lcags la lugs su blugs nas /
NK084(yu)001:1988: lha'i phyag rgya byas pas kyang /
NK084(yu)001:1989: de'i don gyis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol nas /
NK084(yu)001:1990: 'bras bu mya ngan las 'das pa'i go 'phang thob par 'gyur na zhes dape'o //
NK084(yu)001:1991: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK084(yu)001:1992: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK084(yu)001:1993: 'di dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK084(yu)001:1994: chos thams cad rang bzhin myed pa don dam pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1995: kun tu snang gi dngos po thams cad rang bzhin myed pa ye shes sgyu mar byas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1996: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yig 'brur sbyangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1997: phyag rgya gcig pas rang gi lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su sbyangs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:1998: spros pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis spyod yul thams cad
NK084(yu)001:1999: lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du sbyangs nas 'bras
NK084(yu)001:2000: bu thob pa lta ci smos te /
NK084(yu)001:2001: ting nge 'dzin de mngon du gyur pa de kho na nyid 'bras bu ye shes yin pas /
NK084(yu)001:2002: 'bras bu gzhan nas rtsal du gzhan myed do //
NK084(yu)001:2003: de bas na smos ci dgos te de nyid yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2004: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal bskyed la //
NK084(yu)001:2005: de ltar phyag rgya lha'i dkyil 'khor dam tshig pa gsal bar bskyed pa /
NK084(yu)001:2006: de la ye shes lngas dbang skur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2007: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa rdzogs par byas la spyan drangs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2008: dbang bskur byin brlabs rdzogs byas te //
NK084(yu)001:2009: stong gsum nyungs 'brur bzhug tshul du //
NK084(yu)001:2010: ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang der /
NK084(yu)001:2011: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor mi shong zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:2012: lha'i rdzu 'phrul gyis stong gsum gyi stong chen po /
NK084(yu)001:2013: mi 'jed 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad nyungs 'bru gcig gi nang du bcug kyang /
NK084(yu)001:2015: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK084(yu)001:2016: yang chung ngu mi 'gro bar chud pa bzhin du
NK084(yu)001:2017: / ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang der /
NK084(yu)001:2018: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis spyan drangs nas bzhugs nas kyang /
NK084(yu)001:2019: gzhal yas khang cher ma 'phel la /
NK084(yu)001:2020: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor de dag chung ngu 'gribs pa ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2021: de'i phyir na gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ngo mtshar che ba yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2022: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK084(yu)001:2023: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas /
NK084(yu)001:2024: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la /
NK084(yu)001:2025: mchod pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pas mchod par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2026: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK084(yu)001:2028: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor ni
NK084(yu)001:2029: bdag nyid chen po'i rang bzhin lhun grub tu gnas
NK084(yu)001:2031: de yang phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2032: bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po thams cad spyan drangs so //
NK084(yu)001:2033: myi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK084(yu)001:2034: yul gang nas spyan drangs na /
NK084(yu)001:2035: chos kyi dbyings la phan tshun dang yul can lta bu myed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2036: rang bzhin spros bral chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes nyid ye shes lngar snang ba de ni /
NK084(yu)001:2037: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba thams cad bzhugs pa'i gnas yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2038: gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes nyid /
NK084(yu)001:2039: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:2040: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2041: ngo bo gang spyan drang na /
NK084(yu)001:2042: dkyil rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK084(yu)001:2043: 'khor b+hu ta bzhi bcu tham pas skor ba'i 'bu
NK084(yu)001:2044: ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po thams cad spyan drangs
NK084(yu)001:2045: ba'o // rang snang dbyer myed dkyil 'khor la //
NK084(yu)001:2047: rang rig pa'i snang ba las byung dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK084(yu)001:2048: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dbyer med par gcig pa yin la /
NK084(yu)001:2049: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK084(yu)001:2050: dgos ched ci'i phyir spyan drang na /
NK084(yu)001:2051: rig pa la rig pa 'jug /dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa mnyam par sbyor bas so //
NK084(yu)001:2052: de yang rang snang la ye shes kyi lha 'jug
NK084(yu)001:2053: pa'i mtshan nyid dam 'jug lugs ni bdag dang lha
NK084(yu)001:2055: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2056: phyogs bcu dus bzhir 'gro ba'i don yongs su rdzogs
NK084(yu)001:2057: par mdzad pa'i rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa
NK084(yu)001:2058: gnyis po de dag thams cad la /
NK084(yu)001:2059: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor kun tu rdzogs //
NK084(yu)001:2060: bdag gis tshe snga ma'i dus phan cad du lha dang bsnyen pa rdzogs par phul bas na /
NK084(yu)001:2061: nyer bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /da ltar gyi
NK084(yu)001:2062: dus na bdag dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang nye bar
NK084(yu)001:2063: gyur pa dang / rgyal ba de dag 'gro ba'i
NK084(yu)001:2064: don mdzad par thugs dam du zhal gyis bzhes pa
NK084(yu)001:2065: las mi 'da' bar bdag gi don mdzad pa'i phyir
NK084(yu)001:2067: +amo kye tshur sbyor e a ha hi bcom ldan 'das ba ga ban /
NK084(yu)001:2068: ma h+aa thugs rje chen pos ka ru ni ka tri gzigs shig sha ho /
NK084(yu)001:2069: sa ma ya dam tshig la dgongs stom /
NK084(yu)001:2070: dza lha mo bzhi h'u bam ho /
NK084(yu)001:2071: +amo dam tshig gi lha'i thugs ka nas lha mo bzhi 'phros pas /
NK084(yu)001:2072: badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig +amo sku /
NK084(yu)001:2073: +aam badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig +aam gsung /
NK084(yu)001:2074: h'u badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig h'u thugs /
NK084(yu)001:2075: 'og min nas mdun gyi nam ka la ye shes
NK084(yu)001:2076: kyi sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis spyan drangs nas
NK084(yu)001:2077: / dbyar gyi sprin phung ltar 'od zer 'dab 'byor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2078: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin
NK084(yu)001:2079: las dbyer med par gsal ba la rig pa'i me
NK084(yu)001:2081: sku rdo rje dang dbyer myed par gyur cig /gsung
NK084(yu)001:2082: rdo rje dang dbyer myed par gyur cig /thugs rdo
NK084(yu)001:2083: rje dang dbyer med par gyur cig /yon tan rdo
NK084(yu)001:2084: rje dang dbyer myed par gyur cig /
NK084(yu)001:2085: 'phrin las rdo rje dang dbyer myed par gyur cig
NK084(yu)001:2086: /s+w+aa badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig s+w+aa
NK084(yu)001:2087: yon tan / h+aa badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig h+aa 'phrin las //
NK084(yu)001:2088: +amo ye shes lnga badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig h'u sdu ba /
NK084(yu)001:2089: dngos grub skul ba'i sngags so //
NK084(yu)001:2090: nam mkha' ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dngos grub gsol /
NK084(yu)001:2091: +amo ye shes lnga badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig stmo sbyor ba /
NK084(yu)001:2092: dngos grub gsol ba'i dus la bab bo //
NK084(yu)001:2093: +amo ye shes lnga badz+ra rdo rje sa ma ya dam tshig ho dgyes par rol /
NK084(yu)001:2094: dngos grub gsol ba la dgyes par dgongs shig /dzahmh'u
NK084(yu)001:2095: bam hoh phyag rgya bzhis dgug bzhug bya zhing dgyes
NK084(yu)001:2096: pa skyed pa'o // me tog dor la dngos grub gsol //
NK084(yu)001:2097: rig pa'i me tog lha la dor la /
NK084(yu)001:2098: rang la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bskul bar bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2099: gnyis myed thim bzhugs mnyes par bya //
NK084(yu)001:2100: de ltar mdun gyi nam mkha' la byon pa la /
NK084(yu)001:2101: rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK084(yu)001:2102: lha dang bdag dbyer myed par rtogs nas /
NK084(yu)001:2103: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gsol ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:2105: bdag dngos grub ma thob bar du bstan par bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK084(yu)001:2106: ma skyes rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni zhes pas phyag 'tshal la mnyes par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2107: sgyu yum 'phrul yab dra 'brel pa ba'i mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2108: phyag rgya'i don gnas thabs bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2109: dbang de ltar rtogs na po'i yul du gang gyur pa rnams //
NK084(yu)001:2111: mnyam pa'i thabs shes rab ngang du rtogs lta bas gsal ting nge na //
NK084(yu)001:2113: thams cad byang chub rig pa mchog gi rgya //
NK084(yu)001:2115: rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po thabs shes rab dbyer med pa'i don de /
NK084(yu)001:2116: rang rig pa'i mngon sum du gsal ba'i dus na /
NK084(yu)001:2117: phung po dang dbang po dang rnam par shes pa thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:2118: thabs kyi rang bzhin yab kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK084(yu)001:2119: 'byung ba dang yul dang dus thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2120: shes rab kyi rang bzhin yum gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK084(yu)001:2121: de dag thams cad thabs shes rab gnyis su myed
NK084(yu)001:2122: pa byang chub sems mnyam pa'i ngang der rtogs par
NK084(yu)001:2123: gsal na / chos thams cad de ltar rtogs pa'i
NK084(yu)001:2124: ngang de las mi 'da' ba la byang chub mchog
NK084(yu)001:2126: skyod lus kyi yan lag go chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas bzhugs gnas so su //
NK084(yu)001:2127: thabs lha yab yum dang shes rab 'khor bcas thams cad kun //
NK084(yu)001:2129: gsal lha'i skur zhing 'od zer sprul pa 'phro bsgoms na //
NK084(yu)001:2130: rnam pa ji ltar sgom na /
NK084(yu)001:2131: bsgul rang gi lus kyis bskyod cing byas pa thams cad phyag rgya lha'i yin //
NK084(yu)001:2132: sgom pa'i yon tan gang yin na /
NK084(yu)001:2133: skyod chen ni lus kyi yan lag lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:2134: de ltar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas khang bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2135: de'i nang du thabs yab dang shes rab yum thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:2136: de'i 'khor bcas kun bsgom pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2137: dbu' la de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs yab yum bcu /
NK084(yu)001:2138: lag pa g.yas pa la rdo rje'i rigs yab yum bcu /
NK084(yu)001:2139: lag pa g.yon pa la rin po che'i rigs yab yum bcu /
NK084(yu)001:2140: rkang pa g.yas pa la las kyi rigs yab yum bcu /
NK084(yu)001:2141: rkang pa g.yon pa la pad ma'i rigs yab yum bcu bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:2142: de yang rngam klog 'khor lo bkod pa'i mdo' las /
NK084(yu)001:2143: lag g.yas rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
NK084(yu)001:2144: lag g.yon rin chen sems dpa' ste /
NK084(yu)001:2145: rkang g.yas las kyi sems dpa' la //
NK084(yu)001:2146: rkang g.yon pad ma'i sems dpa' yin //
NK084(yu)001:2147: dbus ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs //
NK084(yu)001:2149: sku de dag yang gsal zhing 'od zer 'phro bar bsgoms nas gsal na /
NK084(yu)001:2150: rang gi lus kyis bsgul skyod byas pa thams cad yang lha'i phyag rgya yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2152: rig pa lus kyi yan lag lha yi dam lha'i
NK084(yu)001:2153: skur gsal ba'i ngang las mi 'da' ba'i phyir ro
NK084(yu)001:2154: // gsang de lta bu de ni ba de kho
NK084(yu)001:2155: na nyid nges pa'i don b+ha zhig yin pas las
NK084(yu)001:2157: snying chos thams cad po'i phyag rgya lha'i skur gsal
NK084(yu)001:2158: ba las 'da' de las mi 'da' ba'i phyir na
NK084(yu)001:2159: ka'o // nges tshig ji ltar yin na /
NK084(yu)001:2160: spyod yul thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:2161: skye bo dang theg pa 'og ma thams cad kyi spyod yul du ma gyur pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2162: de ni rgyu 'bras su gnyis su myed pa'i don b+ha zhig yin pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:2163: chos thams cad don gyi snying po'i ngang de las mi 'da' ba'i phyir na 'da' ka'o //
NK084(yu)001:2164: mi bskyod rdo rje sems dpa' nyi ma'i gdan dkyil 'bru lnga yi ge //
NK084(yu)001:2165: rin chen 'byung ldan zla ba'i gdan dkyil 'bru lnga yi ge //
NK084(yu)001:2166: lnga lag pa g.yas g.yon gnyis zung du spros pa bsdus las //
NK084(yu)001:2167: sbyar yab yum thabs shes rab bas phyag 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK084(yu)001:2168: lag pa g.yas pa mi bskyod pa'i rang bzhin gyi
NK084(yu)001:2169: sor mo'i bre ga lnga la nyi ma'i dal sen
NK084(yu)001:2171: de'i steng du gung mo la mdzub mo la h'u /
NK084(yu)001:2175: lag pa g.yon pa rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rang bzhin du bsgoms pa'i /
NK084(yu)001:2176: sor mo'i bre ga lnga la zla ba'i dal sen zlum tsam pa lnga'i steng du /
NK084(yu)001:2183: de ltar gnyis po de nas 'od 'phros pas 'phags pa mchod /
NK084(yu)001:2184: sems can gyi don byas tshur 'dus pa las yi ge bcu la thim pas 'od du 'bar ro //
NK084(yu)001:2185: de thugs khar thal mo sbyar bas yab yum sbyor ba byed par bsam ste /
NK084(yu)001:2186: de ltar yab yum thabs shes rab sbyor byed pa des ni /
NK084(yu)001:2187: phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu rdo rje thal mo yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2188: +amo dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK084(yu)001:2190: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK084(yu)001:2192: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor bas //
NK084(yu)001:2194: bde' ba chen po 'byin pa'i rgya' //phyag rgya'i don bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2195: bdag kun tu bzang po bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2196: mkha' rdo rje rtse lngar bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2198: r+aa prag tu h'u dang a dang ha bsam /
NK084(yu)001:2199: yum kun tu bzang mor bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2202: 'dab ma bzhi la lam mam pam tam bsam /
NK084(yu)001:2203: de nas rdo rje dang pad ma rtse sprad pas /
NK084(yu)001:2206: 'bru brgyad po snol mar rtse sprad pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2207: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor ba byas pas /
NK084(yu)001:2208: bde' ba chen po byang chub kyi sems 'byin pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2209: de ni lhag pa byang chub sems kyis dbang bskur ba'i phyag rgya yin la /
NK084(yu)001:2210: 'dir lag pa g.yas g.yon sor mo snol la rtse sprad la bsgom par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2211: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2212: bcing ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2213: lag pa g.yas pa mi skyod pa'i rang bzhin gyi sor mo'i steng gi /
NK084(yu)001:2214: swa h+aa a'i yig 'bru bzhi khu tshur nang du sbas nas /
NK084(yu)001:2216: mdzub mo sgreng nas phyir la bkan pa'i tshul gyis gzung ba ni dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2217: h'u bsgreng rtse mo rdo rje 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2218: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya ba stan /
NK084(yu)001:2219: mdzub mo sgreng ba'i rtse mo la yi ge h+aum
NK084(yu)001:2220: las rdo rje rtse lnga par bsam pa ni chos
NK084(yu)001:2221: kyi phyag rgya'o // zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2222: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya /
NK084(yu)001:2223: lag pa g.yon pa bzla ba'i dkyil 'khor khu tshur bcangs nas 'bru lnga nang du sbas te /
NK084(yu)001:2224: dril bu bsil zhing rang gi yul la 'khril ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2225: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2226: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK084(yu)001:2227: skur bsgom pa phyag rgya chen po bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2228: yab las kyi rang bzhin yum la 'khril nas /
NK084(yu)001:2229: zhal yum chos kyi rang bzhin la 'dud pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2231: spyir phyag rgya la bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:2232: phyag rgya bca' ba'i gnas lta zur g.yas g.yon no //
NK084(yu)001:2233: phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu rdo rje thal mo'o //
NK084(yu)001:2234: phyag rgya 'byung ba'i thabs thugs ka dang /
NK084(yu)001:2235: phyag rgya dgrol ba'i don stong nyid do //
NK084(yu)001:2236: de la phyag rgya sgyur ba'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:2237: phyi lus kyi yan lag byin gyis barloba pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)001:2238: nang lag pa g.yas g.yon la thabs shes rab kyi yi ge bgod pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2239: gsang ba rdo rje pad ma rtse sprad pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2240: de la nang la bzhi ste /
NK084(yu)001:2241: bcing ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)001:2242: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)001:2243: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK084(yu)001:2244: bsgom pa phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK084(yu)001:2245: de bzhis lha so so'i phyag rgya thams cad khyab par bcing ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2249: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam gnyis po //
NK084(yu)001:2250: dag par dor ba phyag rgya yin //
NK084(yu)001:2253: phyag rgya de dag thams cad gcig tu tshang bar bcings nas byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2254: de bas na thun mong ma yin pa'i phyag rgya zhes bya bar yang 'agro'o //
NK084(yu)001:2255: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2256: bcing ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2257: lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng gi /
NK084(yu)001:2258: lam mam pam tam bzhi khu tshur bcangs nas sbas te /
NK084(yu)001:2259: thugs kar phyir gan du bkan nas bcings pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2261: mum sgreng rtse mo dril bsil 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2263: mdzub mo sgreng ba'i rtse mor yi ge mum bsam /
NK084(yu)001:2265: gcig tu gsal na dril bu bsil ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2266: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2268: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2269: lag pa g.yas pa nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK084(yu)001:2270: gi yig 'bru lnga pos las yab kyi rang bzhin
NK084(yu)001:2272: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2273: bstud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK084(yu)001:2274: sgom pa phyag rgya chen po bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2275: yum gyi dbu la stud de /
NK084(yu)001:2276: zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs dang bcas nas lta'o //
NK084(yu)001:2277: de ltar yum gyi skur lhag gis gsal ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2278: sgom pa phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK084(yu)001:2279: yum de gnyis kyis lha tshogs thams cad 'dre bar shes par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2280: 'bru bzhi ma rtogs pa'i yig 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2281: bcing ba dam tshig gsung yig 'bru sgreng rtse mo 'khor thugs phyag mtshan lo 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2283: zla btul 'bru yum gyi 'bru lnga sbas pa'o sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2284: byed pa las 'khril ba'i tshul gyis skur sgom pa phyag rgya chen po chos la bstan //
NK084(yu)001:2285: 'bru mam lam pyam tam bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bcing ba dam tshig bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2286: lam sgreng rtse mo dril bsil bsam pa chos 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2287: nyi ma dpa' bo 'bru lnga las su 'khril byed pa las kyi /
NK084(yu)001:2288: bstud te 'dzum pa'i mdangs sku phyag rgya chen po kyis lta //
NK084(yu)001:2289: 'bru bzhi h'u am ha bzhi sbas nas thugs bcing ba dam tshig kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2290: swa rtse 'bar ba rin po che //
NK084(yu)001:2292: zla btul byed pa las 'bru sbas dpa' bo dril bsil zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2293: 'khril ba'i sku phyag rgya chen po tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK084(yu)001:2294: 'bru bzhi mam lam pyam tam sbas nas thugs kar
NK084(yu)001:2295: bkan bcing ba dam tshig /mam sgreng rtse mor dril
NK084(yu)001:2297: nyi ma dpa' bo 'bru lnga las su byed pa las kyi 'khril //
NK084(yu)001:2298: stud de 'dzum sku phyag rgya chen po pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK084(yu)001:2299: h'u swa h+aa 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bcing ba dam tshig bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2300: sgreng rtse bsam pa chos mo pad ma 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2301: zla btul dpa' mo 'bru sbas dril bsil byed pa las zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2302: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la sku phyag rgya chen po bstan //
NK084(yu)001:2303: 'bru bzhi dpa' mo sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2304: bcing ba dam tshig /pyam sgreng rtse mo bsam pa chos dril bsil 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2305: nyi ma dpa' bo 'bru lnga las su bcing ba dam tshig 'khril //
NK084(yu)001:2306: bstud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs sku phyag rgya chen po mdangs kyis lta //
NK084(yu)001:2307: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bcing ba dam tshig bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2308: ha sgreng rtse mor bsam pa chos ral gri 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2309: +aa h'u swa zla btul dpa' mo 'bru sbas dril bsil byed pa las zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2310: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la sku phyag rgya chen po bstan //
NK084(yu)001:2311: 'bru mam lam pyam mam bzhi sbas nas thugs bcing ba dam tshig kar bkan //
NK084(yu)001:2312: tam sgreng rtse mo bsam pa chos dril bsil 'bar //
NK084(yu)001:2313: nyi ma dpa' bo 'bru lnga las su byed pa las 'khril //
NK084(yu)001:2314: stud de 'dzum sku phyag rgya chen po pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK084(yu)001:2315: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK084(yu)001:2316: spyir na mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK084(yu)001:2319: de las 'dir ni sems kyis dmigs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2320: nang mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa zer ro //
NK084(yu)001:2321: sems kyis yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK084(yu)001:2322: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK084(yu)001:2323: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du grub pas yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang 'dra bas /
NK084(yu)001:2324: mchod pa mang nyung gi tshad sprin gyi tshogs tsam pa sprul na dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2325: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2326: 'jig rten gyi khams zhing khams su dbul bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2327: de yang ji ltar sprul zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:2328: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK084(yu)001:2330: mnan na nem snyom byed pa /
NK084(yu)001:2331: gteg na 'phar mnyam byed par sprul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2333: zhing khams de'i mtshan nyid ci zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:2335: reg na zag myed kyi bde' ba khyad par can skye ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2336: sna tshogs rin po che'i gzhi'i //
NK084(yu)001:2338: gzhi' rin po che rnam pa sna tshogs las grub pa /
NK084(yu)001:2340: dwangs shing mdzes par snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2341: mdzes par bris shing spras pa dang //
NK084(yu)001:2342: zhing khams de'i rgyan ni ci zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:2343: bar bar du rin po che'i dmig mang ris su bris pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2344: de'i dmyig tu gser gyi sor gdub la /
NK084(yu)001:2346: rin po che'i za rang tshags dang /
NK084(yu)001:2348: chun 'phyang gi lda ldi'i ris su spras pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2349: de lta bu yang dkyil 'khor gyi lha la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2351: 'jig rten gyi ri thams cad tram las rin po che'i phung po /
NK084(yu)001:2352: kha dog mdzes pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan kun ldan
NK084(yu)001:2353: pa 'od 'phro zhing 'od zer 'bar bar dmigs la
NK084(yu)001:2354: dbul lo // dbyibs legs rdzing bu ro mchog bsil //
NK084(yu)001:2356: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi mtsho' dang rdzing bu dang /
NK084(yu)001:2358: chu klung chen po thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:2359: bdud rtsi ro mchog brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK084(yu)001:2360: dbyibs legs pa bsil la 'jam pa'i bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun du dmyigs la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2361: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK084(yu)001:2362: khang pa gzhal yas khang rgyan dang bcas par dbul bar ba stan /
NK084(yu)001:2363: 'jig rten gyi khams na sbra dang gur dang /
NK084(yu)001:2364: khang pa la sogs pa thams cad rnams rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK084(yu)001:2365: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK084(yu)001:2366: phyi nang myed pa dper na shel gyi phor pa
NK084(yu)001:2367: lta bur gsal ba zang thal bar dmyigs la dbul
NK084(yu)001:2368: lo // rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i 'tshal //
NK084(yu)001:2369: 'jig rten gyi khams na rtsi shing ji snyed yod pa rnams /
NK084(yu)001:2370: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing gi 'tshal /
NK084(yu)001:2371: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyan du dmyigs la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2372: glu dbyangs tshigs su ba cad pa'i sgra //
NK084(yu)001:2373: 'jig rten gyi khams na glu len pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2374: dbyangs dang tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra ji snyed yod pa thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:2375: bde' bar gshegs pa la tshigs su bcad pa'i bstod pa byed par bsams la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2376: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK084(yu)001:2377: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi gos kyi rnam pa ji snyed yod pa thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2382: gdugs dang ba dan la sogs par bsams la dbul bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2383: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK084(yu)001:2384: gzugs lha dang lha mor rgyan gyis brgyan nas /
NK084(yu)001:2385: 'jig rten gyi khams na nor bu dang /
NK084(yu)001:2388: rgyan ji snyed yod pa thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2389: bde' bar gshegs pa la dbu' rgyan dang /
NK084(yu)001:2396: rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs par bsams la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2397: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams sna tshogs dang //
NK084(yu)001:2398: 'jig rten gyi khams na gos yod pa rnams ni /
NK084(yu)001:2399: bde' bar gshegs pa la sku'i stod g.yogs dang /
NK084(yu)001:2402: yon tan gyi chos gos dang /
NK084(yu)001:2403: mdzad pa las kyi phu dung dang /
NK084(yu)001:2405: sked chings nor bu'i rtsar 'phyong la sogs pa dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2406: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK084(yu)001:2407: 'jig rten gyi khams na bza' ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2411: ldag pa'i longs spyod ji snyed yod pa thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2412: bde' bar gshegs pa la ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa'i bdud rtsir bsams la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2413: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2414: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyi //
NK084(yu)001:2415: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK084(yu)001:2416: 'jig rten gyi khams na skyes pa dang bud myed dang /
NK084(yu)001:2419: ji snyed yod pa thams cad /
NK084(yu)001:2420: rang rang gi rgyan mdzes par brgyan pa /
NK084(yu)001:2421: grangs bsam gyis mi khyab pa nam mkha'i rdul phra mo snyed dang grangs mnyam pa /
NK084(yu)001:2422: de dag thams cad kyang rkang pas stabs mdzes pa'i bro brdung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2423: lag pas phyag rgya mdzes pa'i gar byed par bsams la dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2424: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK084(yu)001:2425: gong ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa des /
NK084(yu)001:2426: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang bar dmigs la /
NK084(yu)001:2427: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK084(yu)001:2428: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs re re zhing la rgyas par dbul bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2429: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK084(yu)001:2430: rims kyis yang na cig char du //
NK084(yu)001:2431: tshad dang dbul thabs bstan pa /
NK084(yu)001:2432: dbul ba'i thabs ni ma h+aa yo ga'i sgor zhugs
NK084(yu)001:2433: pa'i rnal 'byor pa de ni sangs rgya ba'i skal
NK084(yu)001:2435: de la ting nge 'dzin gsal mi gsal gyi khyad par gyis /
NK084(yu)001:2436: mchod pa yang gsal na cig char du dbul la /
NK084(yu)001:2437: mi gsal na rims kyis dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2438: blo che na cig char ram dus gcig la dbul la /
NK084(yu)001:2439: blo chung na rims kyis dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2440: blo shin tu chung na rim pa'am mos pas dbul bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2441: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK084(yu)001:2442: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK084(yu)001:2443: nam mkhas gar khyab par chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab /
NK084(yu)001:2444: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par bde' bar gshegs pas na /
NK084(yu)001:2445: mchod pa dang bde' bar gshegs pa mnyam par sbyor zhing dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2446: de ni rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i mchod pa myin
NK084(yu)001:2447: ting nge 'dzin gyis 'bul bas na mchod pa'i phyag
NK084(yu)001:2449: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK084(yu)001:2450: rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2451: thog ma ni bdag dang gzhan gnyis las /
NK084(yu)001:2452: thog mar bdag ba sgral lo //
NK084(yu)001:2453: bdag nyid ni rang lus so //
NK084(yu)001:2454: rtogs pa ni dbang po yul gyi sgrol ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:2455: yul du snang ba thams cad yum gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK084(yu)001:2456: shes pa 'jug pa thams cad yab kyi dkyil 'khor bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:2457: bsgom pa ni rang lus skye ba myed par sgom /
NK084(yu)001:2458: ma rig pa dang log lta dang bdag 'dzin la
NK084(yu)001:2459: sogs pa phyin ci log gi snang ba gang yin
NK084(yu)001:2460: pa thams cad mchod par dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2461: de nas gnyis myed blo yis ni //
NK084(yu)001:2462: thugs rjes gzhan sgral ba bstan /
NK084(yu)001:2463: de ltar rtogs pas bdag ba sgral ba de nas /
NK084(yu)001:2464: thugs rjes gzhan ba sgral ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2465: bdag rnal 'byor pa dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2466: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i don rtogs pa'i /
NK084(yu)001:2469: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK084(yu)001:2470: blo chung ba'am sems gnyis su myed pa'i gnyis su
NK084(yu)001:2471: 'dzin pa de dag /snying rje chen po'i yul du
NK084(yu)001:2472: dmyigs la / 'jig rten na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad snying rje'i 'du shes kyis /
NK084(yu)001:2473: gnyis su myed par bsgral bar bya //
NK084(yu)001:2474: bdag nyid sgrol ba'i lha ta ki ra tsar gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2475: gri 'jam dpal ye shes sems dpar gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2476: bsgral ba'i sems can thams cad de dag tu ru tra gsal bar byas la /
NK084(yu)001:2477: bdag tu rtog pa rtsad nas bcad nas /
NK084(yu)001:2478: sems 'og min du bsgral ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2479: phung po 'dod yon gyi lha mor byas la /
NK084(yu)001:2480: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la dbul bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2481: de bas na bdag dang gzhan gnyis su myed par bsgral bar bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2482: gsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs la //
NK084(yu)001:2483: sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni lnga las /
NK084(yu)001:2484: 'di mngon du phyung ba sbyor ba'i mchod pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:2485: de yang yum de rang gi ting nge 'dzin bsgom shes na gsal ldan ma zhes bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:2486: rnal 'byor pas byin gyis brlabs mi dgos /
NK084(yu)001:2487: ting nge 'dzin bsgom mi shes na /
NK084(yu)001:2488: rnal 'byor pas byin gyis brlabs la bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2489: thabs yab dang shes rab yum gnyis myed pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2490: thabs yab rdo rje sems dpar bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2491: mkha' rdo rje rtse lnga par sgom /
NK084(yu)001:2495: shes rab yum dbyings phyug mar bskyed /
NK084(yu)001:2496: mkha' pad ma 'dab brgyad du bsam /
NK084(yu)001:2497: dkyil du h'u dgod par bya /
NK084(yu)001:2498: yab yum gnyis myed du sbyor ba byed pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2499: yum gyis sa ma ya ho /
NK084(yu)001:2501: sa ma ya h'u zhes brdas skul /
NK084(yu)001:2502: yab kyis ra ga ya ho /
NK084(yu)001:2504: 'khril sbyor ba ba'i mchod chen mnyam dus gsum sangs rgyas dang sbyor bas //
NK084(yu)001:2505: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i mchod pa mdzad nas /
NK084(yu)001:2506: rig pa nang du bzung bas /
NK084(yu)001:2509: lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2510: dga' bral gyi dga' ba chen pos rang lus bde' bas rgyas par bya /
NK084(yu)001:2511: de nas byang sems phyir byung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2512: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK084(yu)001:2513: lhag pa byang chub sems phar la 'phros pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod pa'i phul /
NK084(yu)001:2514: bdag nyid yab yum la thim pas /
NK084(yu)001:2515: rang gi rtog tshogs nyid dkyil 'khor du gsal ba la mnyes pa'i mchod pa dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2516: spyir sgrol ba'i mchod pa la lnga ste /
NK084(yu)001:2517: rang bzhin gyis sgrol ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2521: mngon du phyung ba'i dang lnga las /
NK084(yu)001:2523: dang po ni phung po khams dang skye mched thams cad don dam par ma skyes pa /
NK084(yu)001:2524: kun rdzob tu ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2525: de bas na mchog gi mchod pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2526: mchod pa thams cad kyi thog mar 'gro ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2527: rang rig pa nyid rtogs nas /
NK084(yu)001:2528: ma rig pa'i mun pa rnams mchod par 'bul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2529: don gyi ngo bo la sgrol bar ma gyur ba'am /
NK084(yu)001:2530: mchod par ma gyur pa gang yang myed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2531: mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas chen po dag /bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs dbul //
NK084(yu)001:2532: rdzas kyi mchod pa ni gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:2534: grub pa bzhis rgyan pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2537: dri chen dri chu mam sa rag ta lhag pa'i byang sems dang lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:2538: grub pa bzhis rgyan pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2539: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2540: chos can ngo bos grub pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2541: mthu' can las kyis grub pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2542: byin brlabs nus pas grub pa'i rdzas so //
NK084(yu)001:2543: de lta bu'i grub rdzas chen po ni /
NK084(yu)001:2545: las kyis mnyam pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:2547: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' dang /
NK084(yu)001:2548: lha ye shes sems dpa' mnyam zhing dbyer myed pa'i tshogs la /
NK084(yu)001:2549: mchod pa bla na myed pa'i dam rdzas dag pa'i mchod pa 'bul ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2550: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo' //rgyu'i rdzas /
NK084(yu)001:2551: bza' ba zas kyi rnam pa /
NK084(yu)001:2552: bca' ba zus pa'i rnam pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2553: btung ba chang gi rnam pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2554: bgo' ba gos kyi rnam pa rnams ni /
NK084(yu)001:2555: longs spyod rdzas kyi mchod pa chen por dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2556: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad kun //
NK084(yu)001:2558: dmyig gzugs kyi longs spyod dang /
NK084(yu)001:2561: lce ro lus reg bya'i longs spyod dang /
NK084(yu)001:2562: lnga ni rang la gang yod ldan na dngos su dbul /
NK084(yu)001:2563: ma ldan na ting nge 'dzin gyis sprul la dbul te /
NK084(yu)001:2564: longs spyod lnga po thams cad kun dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2565: dkyil 'khor ye shes lha'i la ni dkyil 'khor mchod pa lha mo'i thim //
NK084(yu)001:2567: ye shes lha'i dkyil 'khor dbul bya la /
NK084(yu)001:2568: 'bul byed bdag gi thugs ka nas 'dod yon lha mo mang po spros nas thim pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2569: de la ni ye shes la ye shes rol zhes bya /
NK084(yu)001:2570: chos nyid la chos nyid thim zhes bya /
NK084(yu)001:2571: lha la lha rol zhes bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2572: a li u li sngags kyis dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2573: +amo phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2574: sku lngar mngon pa nyid yi ge +amo de'i phyir 'go' drangs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2575: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku la bstod pa /
NK084(yu)001:2576: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i lha /
NK084(yu)001:2577: gnas dang dus kun tu thugs dam gyi dbang gis 'gro ba'i don rdzogs par mdzad pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2578: rgyal ba yab yum lnga yang sku lngar 'dus /
NK084(yu)001:2579: rang 'byung ye shes nyid rang 'byung la ma 'gags par gsal ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2580: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK084(yu)001:2581: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK084(yu)001:2582: chos kyi sku la bstod pa /
NK084(yu)001:2583: ye shes lnga mi rtog pa'i ye shes su gsal ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2584: dkyil 'khor de nyid khyab brdal chen por gnas pa ni thig le'o //
NK084(yu)001:2585: de yang chos nyid kyi sku ni spros pa'i mtshan ma thams cad bral ba'i chos nyid yin te /
NK084(yu)001:2588: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la bstod pa /
NK084(yu)001:2589: gang yang ma spangs par zag pa myed pa'i bsod nams rang snang ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2591: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs las nges par 'byung
NK084(yu)001:2592: ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe' byad
NK084(yu)001:2593: du ldan pa'o // rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs bar
NK084(yu)001:2594: chad myed pa las 'bras bu nges par 'byung ba
NK084(yu)001:2595: du ldan pa'o // ni / longs sku de dag
NK084(yu)001:2596: las 'khor sprul sku'i tshogs 'gro ba rigs drug gi
NK084(yu)001:2597: don sprul sku mang por mdzad do //
NK084(yu)001:2598: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs ho //
NK084(yu)001:2599: sprul pa'i sku la bstod pa /
NK084(yu)001:2600: snang ba rtags stong pa don /
NK084(yu)001:2601: de gnyis su med pas thig le /
NK084(yu)001:2602: kun tu rdzogs pas gnyis su myed pas brag cha lta bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:2603: de sku gsung thugs dbyer med pa rang gi ngo
NK084(yu)001:2604: bo mnyam pa nyid 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral
NK084(yu)001:2605: bar rang bzhin gyis grub pa ni rdo rje'i sku'o
NK084(yu)001:2606: // de sku lnga la dgyes pas na ho zhes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2607: +amo rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK084(yu)001:2608: chos sku skye myed don gyi gsung /
NK084(yu)001:2609: longs sku dgongs pa brda'i gsung /
NK084(yu)001:2610: gsung lngar mngon pa nyid yi ge mo de'i phyir mgo drangs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2611: rdo rje bsod nams kyi ngo bo sgra ma spangs pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:2613: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku nyid /
NK084(yu)001:2614: phyag dang zhabs dang spyan dang ljags kyi brdas /
NK084(yu)001:2615: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor la brda go ba sprod pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2616: sgrib pa sel bas na rdo rje /
NK084(yu)001:2617: 'bras bu ye shes kyi bsod nams las grub pas na longs sku'o //
NK084(yu)001:2619: spros pa myed pa'i thig le brjod du myed pas /
NK084(yu)001:2620: don gyi gsung chen pos te chos kyi skur gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2621: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK084(yu)001:2622: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku rig pa sgyu ma'i gsung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2624: ye shes ni stong pa'i don shes pa /
NK084(yu)001:2626: ldan pa ni stong pa'i don ye shes su ldan pa /
NK084(yu)001:2627: ye shes dkyil 'khor du ldan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2628: de lta bu des ma brjod par thams cad gsal
NK084(yu)001:2629: bar brda sprod pa'i phyir na rig pa'i gsung ngo
NK084(yu)001:2630: // de ni mngon par byang chub pa'i gsung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2631: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK084(yu)001:2632: sprul sku sna tshogs tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2633: rdo rje stong pa sgra chen tshangs pa'i gsung /
NK084(yu)001:2634: mtha' yas sna tshogs su snang ba ste sprul pa'i sku'i tshangs pa'i gsung gis /
NK084(yu)001:2635: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad kyis go bar spyod pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2636: de dag gi nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa thams cad gtan nas 'joms par byed do //
NK084(yu)001:2637: gcig la mang po grags pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:2639: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che ho //
NK084(yu)001:2640: rdo rje'i sku grags stong dbyer myed kyi gsung //
NK084(yu)001:2641: gsung grags stong dbyer myed nyid kyis thams cad la dbang du bsgyur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2642: grags stong ni so so'i spyod pa thams cad dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:2643: tshig myed pa nyid brjod pa dang 'dra bar gsal ba gsung gi rang bzhin yin pas na /
NK084(yu)001:2645: de lta bu'i don la dgyes pas na ho zhes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2646: +amo sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK084(yu)001:2649: sku ni chos sku zag bral te /
NK084(yu)001:2650: de'i thugs ni mnyam pa chen po yin la /
NK084(yu)001:2651: de nyid chos kyi ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:2652: gsung ni mngon par byang chub pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:2653: mi g.yo' ba'i thugs yin la /
NK084(yu)001:2654: de ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:2655: thugs ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ste /
NK084(yu)001:2656: mye long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK084(yu)001:2659: de gsum dbyer myed pas na rdzogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2660: mchog tu gyur pas na chen por gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2661: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK084(yu)001:2664: yon tan ni rdo rje'i thugs te /
NK084(yu)001:2665: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:2666: 'phrin las ni 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs te /
NK084(yu)001:2667: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK084(yu)001:2668: de rnams gcig tu gnas pas na kun tu rdzogs zhes so //
NK084(yu)001:2669: ye nas sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las nyer lngar rdzogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2670: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK084(yu)001:2671: rigs lnga'i thugs ni ye shes lngar gnas te /
NK084(yu)001:2672: de yang de re re la yang ye shes lnga
NK084(yu)001:2673: lngar lhun gyis grub par gnas pas na ye nas
NK084(yu)001:2675: ma btsal bar sku lnga ye nas lhun grub tu rdzogs pa na /
NK084(yu)001:2676: rang bzhin kun tu bzang po zhes de la bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2677: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che ho /
NK084(yu)001:2678: sems dpa' dang sems ma thams cad kyang /
NK084(yu)001:2679: rang rang gi rigs kyi ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du 'dus pas na /
NK084(yu)001:2680: rdzogs zhes bya ba'i rgyal ba nyid dang dbyer myed pa'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:2682: de lta bu la dgyes pas na ho zhes bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2683: chos kyi dbyings dang rang rig pa'i ngo bo nyid dmigs pa nyid /
NK084(yu)001:2684: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang du shar ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:2685: de phyi nang myed par gsal ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:2686: ye shes rin po che'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2687: myi dmyigs pa'i rig pa nyid sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs su snang bas /
NK084(yu)001:2688: snang stong dbyer myed mnyam pa'i dbyings phyi nang dang rgya che chung myed pa'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK084(yu)001:2689: +amo myi dmyigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK084(yu)001:2692: chos kyi dbyings ni ye nas rang gi ngo bos snang stong dbyer myed par mnyam pas te /
NK084(yu)001:2693: des thams cad du khyab pa ni nam mkha' dang
NK084(yu)001:2694: mnyam pa mu mtha' myed pa'i phyir sangs rgyas kyi
NK084(yu)001:2695: zhing ngo // de lta bu'i gzhal yas khang de ni /
NK084(yu)001:2696: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bzhugs gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:2697: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs 'phro //
NK084(yu)001:2699: mtha' yas kun nas ni sku'i gnas kyi ba spu'i bu ga gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:2700: sna tshogs 'phro ni 'od zer bsam gyis myi khyab
NK084(yu)001:2701: pa 'phros pas khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad
NK084(yu)001:2702: kyi sgrib pa ma lus pa sbyong bar byed pa'o
NK084(yu)001:2703: // mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK084(yu)001:2704: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i longs spyod thams cad ni /
NK084(yu)001:2705: mchod pa'i lha mo lngar lhun gyis grub nas mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2706: lha la lha thim zhes bya'o /
NK084(yu)001:2707: de yang mtha' yas pa'i 'dod yon kun la myong
NK084(yu)001:2708: ba myed pa'i tshul gyis spyod pas na longs spyod
NK084(yu)001:2709: pa'o // sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po ho //
NK084(yu)001:2712: seng ge la sogs pa 'bras bu'i byang chub sems
NK084(yu)001:2713: dpa' re re yang brgyad brgyad du snang nas rgyal
NK084(yu)001:2715: sku snang la rang bzhin myed pa'am gsal ba nyi zla dang /
NK084(yu)001:2716: gsung nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pas pad ma'i gdan dang /
NK084(yu)001:2717: thugs rigs pa'i ye shes su rang snang ba'i brtags
NK084(yu)001:2718: su dgos 'dod 'byung ba rin po che'i gdan no
NK084(yu)001:2719: // +amo phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK084(yu)001:2721: 'phrin las lnga tshogs pa'i phyir +amo gyis sna drangs nas so //
NK084(yu)001:2722: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams ni /
NK084(yu)001:2723: mang nyu nga gi tshad rdul phra rab dang mnyam
NK084(yu)001:2724: pas na sems can yang rdul phra rab dang mnyam
NK084(yu)001:2725: pa de rnams ni don bya'i yul lo //
NK084(yu)001:2726: de yang gdul bya'i gnas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten tshad rdul phra rab dang /
NK084(yu)001:2727: ngo bo dag pa dang ma dag pa'i gdul bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2728: de dag ni nyon mongs pa zhi bar byed pas na zhi ba'i 'phrin las so //
NK084(yu)001:2729: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK084(yu)001:2731: de dag tu rgyal ba'i sprul pas 'gro ba'i don byed pa yang rdul phra rab dang mnyam pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2732: de bas na rgyal ba'i don rnams ni 'dul byed do //
NK084(yu)001:2733: rdul phran snyed ni 'dul thabs so //
NK084(yu)001:2734: de rnams 'gro don dpag tu mdzad pas na /
NK084(yu)001:2736: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK084(yu)001:2739: bde' bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa thub pa drug gis /
NK084(yu)001:2741: 'dul thabs zhi khro sna tshogs su snang bas bsam yas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2742: de rnams kyis 'gro ba rnams dbang du byed pas na dbang gi 'phrin las so //
NK084(yu)001:2743: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK084(yu)001:2747: skad cig gam yud tsam mam thang cig gis don byed pa de na drag po'o //
NK084(yu)001:2748: btul ba'i tshad ni ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las so //
NK084(yu)001:2749: de yang don mdzad pas de ma thag pa'i 'phrin
NK084(yu)001:2750: las kyis ji ltar btul ba bzhin du lhun gyis
NK084(yu)001:2752: drag po dang lhun grub kyi 'phrin las so //
NK084(yu)001:2753: +amo thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK084(yu)001:2754: 'khor 'das kyi dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sku gsung thugs su gnas la /
NK084(yu)001:2755: sku gsung thugs kyi rol pas yon tan 'phrin las su rang shar te /
NK084(yu)001:2756: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lngar gnas so //
NK084(yu)001:2757: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK084(yu)001:2758: de ltar sku gsung thugs kyang rig pa'i ye shes kyi bdag nyid du rang shar ba yin te /
NK084(yu)001:2759: de dag gi ngo bo ni bdag nyid chen po dpal kun tu bzang po'o //
NK084(yu)001:2760: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK084(yu)001:2761: bdag nyid chen pos thams cad la khyab pa ltar gnas pa nyid na des ci mdzad zhe na /
NK084(yu)001:2762: 'khor 'das rnams la khyab par mdzad pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2763: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho //
NK084(yu)001:2764: sku gsung thugs kyis kyang dngos po thams cad la ma khyab pa gang yang myed do //
NK084(yu)001:2765: thams cad la khyab kyang bdag nyid chen por sbyor ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:2766: spros pa thams cad dang bral bas na thig le che zhes bya ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2767: de lta bu'i don la dgyes pas na ho zhes gsungs so //
NK084(yu)001:2768: sgyu 'phrul dra bar mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:2769: sgyu yum ste chos kyi dbyings /
NK084(yu)001:2770: 'phrul yab ste ma 'gags par snang ba /
NK084(yu)001:2771: dra ba 'brel pa ste thabs shes rab zung du 'brel pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2772: mngon rdzogs ni ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i rig pa la mngon du rdzogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2773: ting nge 'dzin bstan pa'i yon tan /
NK084(yu)001:2775: de ltar lha'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar rdzogs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2776: shin tu ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa'i
NK084(yu)001:2777: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po pho mo rnams
NK084(yu)001:2780: rnam par snang mdzad kyi dngos grub /
NK084(yu)001:2782: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyi yan
NK084(yu)001:2783: lag lnga la tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK084(yu)001:2784: bar bsgoms la / rkang pas bro brdung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2785: lag pas gar bya ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2786: yid kyis lha rnams la byang chub sems 'phros pas /
NK084(yu)001:2787: lha'i sku gsung thugs mnyes pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2788: sems can gyi don byas nas tshur la 'dus pas /
NK084(yu)001:2789: bdag gis dngos grub thob pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2791: tshe 'dir nam mkha' la bya bazhinadu 'phur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2792: sa la byi bzhin du 'dzul ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2793: chu la mi 'bying ba'i dngos grub 'thob bo //
NK084(yu)001:2795: glu tshig sgra yi phyag rgya yis //
NK084(yu)001:2796: rnal 'byor pa pho mo rnams lta ba dang ting
NK084(yu)001:2797: nge 'dzin gsal bas rdo rje'i glu blang ba dang
NK084(yu)001:2798: / don ldan rdo rje yi tshig gis bde bar
NK084(yu)001:2799: gshegs pa mnyes par byed pa las mi 'da' ba'i
NK084(yu)001:2801: snang ba mtha' yas gsung gi /chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK084(yu)001:2802: chos nyid kyi gsung dang bstan pa thams cad dus gcig tu mkhyen pa'i dngos grub 'thob bo //
NK084(yu)001:2803: rgyan dang bgo' ba'i yo byad /
NK084(yu)001:2804: rgyan dang bgo' ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK084(yu)001:2805: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams lhar gsal ba las /
NK084(yu)001:2806: lus la rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs gdags pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2807: dar dang za 'og la sogs pa'i gos sna tshogs bgo ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2810: longs spyod de'i yon tan ni /
NK084(yu)001:2811: sku gang gis kyang zil gyis mi non pa'i dngos grub 'thob pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2812: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad /
NK084(yu)001:2813: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK084(yu)001:2814: rnal 'byor pa rnams longs spyod thams cad bdud rtsi'am
NK084(yu)001:2815: 'dod yon gyi lha mor byin gyis rlabs nas bza'
NK084(yu)001:2816: btung longs spyod nas phul zhing dngos grub blangs pa
NK084(yu)001:2817: yis / rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dngos grub /
NK084(yu)001:2818: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK084(yu)001:2819: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che dang 'dra ba'i sku /
NK084(yu)001:2820: longs spyod thams cad bdud rtsir 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:2821: a li ka li'i yo byad /
NK084(yu)001:2822: a li ka li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK084(yu)001:2823: sgrol ba dang sbyor ba'i mchod pa tshul bzhin du phul la /
NK084(yu)001:2824: thabs shes rab gnyis snyoms 'jug gi phyag rgyar gyur
NK084(yu)001:2825: pas thabs shes rab gnyis su myed par gnas pa
NK084(yu)001:2826: de yang / don yod grub pa'i dngos grub /
NK084(yu)001:2828: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i dngos grub thams cad tshul bzhin du 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:2829: de yang chad sbyor lam bstan no //
NK084(yu)001:2832: gong du bskyed pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i bzlas pa
NK084(yu)001:2833: bya ba yang phar 'phro ba dang tshul bstud pa'i
NK084(yu)001:2835: bdag las ye shes kyi lha mdun du dabye'o //
NK084(yu)001:2836: rnam gsum tshul gyis ma 'khrul bar //
NK084(yu)001:2837: bdag dam tshig gi lha gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2838: mdun na ye shes kyi lha gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2839: bar du sngags kyi 'phro 'du gsal ba ste /
NK084(yu)001:2842: sngags bzlas pas phar 'phros pas ye shes lha'i thugs dam bskul ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2843: slar 'dus pas bdag la dngos grub gsol bar dmyigs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2845: rnam par rtog pas mi gcad pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2846: sngags kyi bar myi tshig gis mi gcad par bzlas par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2847: 'dris gsal brtan pa mchog gis bya //
NK084(yu)001:2848: de yang rang lha'i rnal 'byor la 'dris pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2850: rnam par rtog pa'i rlung gis ma skyod par brtan par bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2851: de ni mchog gi bzlas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2852: de la bzlas pa la gsum ste /
NK084(yu)001:2856: dang po ni mdun gyi bar snang la /
NK084(yu)001:2857: brum bi sha bi shud d+he badz+ra gnya' na tsag
NK084(yu)001:2858: sur r+ya rad na pad ma ma d+ha la zhes
NK084(yu)001:2859: brjod pas gzhal yas khang bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:2860: de nas lha dbye' ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2861: h'u zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK084(yu)001:2862: h'u dang pos snang srid gsal bar byas /
NK084(yu)001:2863: h'u gnyis pas thams cad bdag la bsdus /
NK084(yu)001:2864: h'u gsum pas bdag dam tshig pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2865: lha ye shes pa gnyis su dbye' ste /
NK084(yu)001:2866: bdag dam tshig gi lha'i dkyil 'khor mdun na /
NK084(yu)001:2867: lha ye shes pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal te /
NK084(yu)001:2868: mar me gcig las gnyis su dbye' ba ltar bsam mo //
NK084(yu)001:2878: spyi bsnyen ni rigs thams cad rdo rje sems dpa' 'dus pas /
NK084(yu)001:2879: h'u badz+ra 'drig /mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK084(yu)001:2882: bo de tsi ta ma ha su ka gnya' na d+ha du a zhes bzlas so //
NK084(yu)001:2884: lha rang rang gi sngags thad kar bzlas so //
NK084(yu)001:2886: phyi lus dmyigs pa'i bzlas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2887: nang rtsa la dmyigs pa'i bzlas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2888: gsang ba mkha' dbyings la dmyigs pa'i bzlas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2890: bdag gi thugs kha na nyi zla pad ma'i gdan /
NK084(yu)001:2891: de'i steng na rdo rje sems dpa' tshon gang ba /
NK084(yu)001:2892: g.yas gser gyi rdo rje nas tsam pa /
NK084(yu)001:2893: g.yon g.yu'i dril bu khu 'phangs tsam 'dzin pa /
NK084(yu)001:2894: sku stod dar dkar gser gyi ngang ris can gyi sku'i stod gsol ba /
NK084(yu)001:2895: sku smad pa ti smug po'i gsung gi smad dkris gsol ba /
NK084(yu)001:2896: dar chen sa dar ris kyis thugs kyi zi'u ldir gsol ba /
NK084(yu)001:2897: rdur kha ngang myig ris kyi yon tan gyi chos gos gsol ba /
NK084(yu)001:2898: chu dar sngon pos mdzad pa las kyi phu rung byas pa /
NK084(yu)001:2899: rin po che'i rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs pas spras pa /
NK084(yu)001:2900: 'od dang 'od zer dpag tu myed pa 'phro ba bsams la /
NK084(yu)001:2902: de'i steng na rdo rje nas tsam pa /
NK084(yu)001:2903: de'i lte ba la h'u mthing ka nyungs 'bru tsam pa /
NK084(yu)001:2904: de'i mtha' ma na phar la sngags kyis skor bar bsam /
NK084(yu)001:2905: mdun du yang de ltar bsams la /
NK084(yu)001:2906: bzlas pa'i bdag dang mdun gyi gnyis la spro bsdu bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2908: bdag gi spyi bo bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK084(yu)001:2909: mgrin pa longs spyod na bcu drug /snying ka chos kyi 'khor lo na brgyad /
NK084(yu)001:2910: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK084(yu)001:2911: gsang gnas rlung gi 'khor lo gzhu' lta bu dang lnga la /
NK084(yu)001:2916: gsang bar don grub rnams bsgom /
NK084(yu)001:2917: de dag gi thugs khar ye shes pa re re /
NK084(yu)001:2918: de'i thugs khar rdo rje dang 'khor lo sogs pa'i phyag mtshan /
NK084(yu)001:2919: de'i lte ba la h'u dang la sogs pa'i rang rang gi sngags kyis skor ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2920: de la dmyigs nas bzlas pas 'od gzer bdag las chad /
NK084(yu)001:2921: spyi bor phog /byang sems gzhu' mgrin par babs /
NK084(yu)001:2922: de nas snying ka /de nas lte ba /
NK084(yu)001:2923: de nas gsang gnas su byung /
NK084(yu)001:2924: phyir 'phros bdag gi spyi bor phog /de bzhin du 'gal me bzhin du bya'o //
NK084(yu)001:2925: gsang ba ltar bzlas pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2926: bdag gis bzlas pa byas pas /
NK084(yu)001:2927: thugs kha'i sngags srog rtsa nas na yar la song /
NK084(yu)001:2934: spro bsdu' ni bsnyen pa'i dus su 'od dkar po phar la nyi rtse ba spro /
NK084(yu)001:2935: nye bsnyen gyi dus su 'od ser po phar la 'phros pa'i 'gro ba'i sgrib pa sbyong /
NK084(yu)001:2936: bsgrub pa'i dus su 'od dmar po phar la 'phros pas sems can gyi sgrib pa sbyong /
NK084(yu)001:2937: tshur 'dus nas dngos grub sdud do //
NK084(yu)001:2938: bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su 'od ljang khu phar
NK084(yu)001:2939: la mi spro bar tshur la sku gsung thugs kyi
NK084(yu)001:2940: dngos grub thams cad bsdud do //
NK084(yu)001:2942: grangs kyi bsnyen pa 'bum tsho drug /dus kyi bsnyen pa dbang po rab zla ba drug /
NK084(yu)001:2944: tha ma zla ba bcu drug go //
NK084(yu)001:2945: mtshan ma ni rab yi dam lha'i zhal mthong /
NK084(yu)001:2947: tha ma nyams dang rmi lam gsal lo //
NK084(yu)001:2948: skyon ni ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2949: bzlas pa sgra ma dag pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2953: shes lta ba rgyu 'jug bsgom pa lam mtshan gzhi lam nyid 'bras bu 'byor pa'i 'brel pa gzungs //
NK084(yu)001:2954: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu smin 'bras bu byed rgyu dang lam rkyen //
NK084(yu)001:2955: gzhi' shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2958: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2960: mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni 'bras bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:2962: gzhi' dang lam ni shes bya dang shes byed kyi 'brel pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:2963: lam dang 'bras bu ni thob byed kyi 'brel ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:2964: de la gzhi' shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:2965: lta ba bden pa dbyer myed /
NK084(yu)001:2966: rig pa sbyor yul dang bral /
NK084(yu)001:2967: skor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2968: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid sgom pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:2969: rang rang gi lus rtog tshogs 'bu ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las /
NK084(yu)001:2970: ye shes kyi lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bsgoms pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2971: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK084(yu)001:2972: lam gyi ting nge 'dzin nus pa mthu' can du gyur pas /
NK084(yu)001:2973: nye sbyor gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK084(yu)001:2974: mthar thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga lhun grub bo //
NK084(yu)001:2975: de bas na gzhi' dang lam du 'byor /
NK084(yu)001:2981: thob pa de kho na smin byed do //
NK084(yu)001:2983: nus mthu' can du gang gyur pa //
NK084(yu)001:2985: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK084(yu)001:2987: lam gyi ting nge 'dzin nus pa mthu' can du gyur pa de la 'bras bu zhes btags la /
NK084(yu)001:2988: gzhan nas 'ongs pa ma yin no //
NK084(yu)001:2990: dang po de las byung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:2991: bar du de'i bya ba byed pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:2994: rnam par dag pa'i yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK084(yu)001:2997: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin kho na 'grub bo //
NK084(yu)001:3002: rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK084(yu)001:3003: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK084(yu)001:3007: rang lus kyi rnam pa lha'i skur smin pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:3009: tshe la dbang ba ni rang don du lo stong drug brgya bzhugs nas /
NK084(yu)001:3010: gzhan don mdzad dgos pa byung ba na brgya' brgya
NK084(yu)001:3011: na mar la mnur nas byis pa lo brgyad pa
NK084(yu)001:3014: lus lha sku dang khyad par myed pa ste /
NK084(yu)001:3015: lus rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gzugs su gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3016: lhun grub ni rgyal ba nyid dang mnyam pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3017: de nas sku lnga lhun grub la sbyor bar byed de /
NK084(yu)001:3018: rnam smin gyi rig 'dzin ni lam gyi 'bras bu'o //
NK084(yu)001:3019: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas dkyil 'khor kun //
NK084(yu)001:3020: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas tshogs bya /
NK084(yu)001:3024: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor rang la bsdu' /
NK084(yu)001:3025: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol /
NK084(yu)001:3026: h'u zhes brjod cing thugs kar bsdu' //bdag nyid gtso' bo'i thugs ka nas h'u 'phros pas /
NK084(yu)001:3027: lha dang gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa thams cad 'od du zhu nas /
NK084(yu)001:3028: gtso' bo'i thugs khar thim pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3029: skye myed mnyam rdzogs dbyings su thim //
NK084(yu)001:3030: bdag nyid kyang 'od du zhu nas chos kyi dbyings
NK084(yu)001:3031: skye ba myed pa'i ngang du thim par gyur to
NK084(yu)001:3032: // de ni stong pa'i go cha ste /
NK084(yu)001:3034: de ni rtag pa yi mtha' dang bral ba'i phyir na /
NK084(yu)001:3035: rdzogs pa'i rim pa sgom pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3036: stong pa'i go chas lus bsrung ste //
NK084(yu)001:3037: de ltar bsgom pa ni stong pa'i go chas te /
NK084(yu)001:3039: de nas kam las rdo rje'i go khrab dang /
NK084(yu)001:3042: h+aum las rin po che'i thag pa re gung 'dzug la bsams la bcing ngo //
NK084(yu)001:3043: rad na ma le a be shin tsa zhes pas rin po che'i phreng bas bcing ngo //
NK084(yu)001:3044: pa ta lam zhes pas dar spyangs dkar po g.yas su 'phur ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:3045: a bi shin tsa mam zhes pas dar spyangs dmar po g.yon du 'phur ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3046: spyod lam kun tu brtsal myed par //
NK084(yu)001:3047: dus kun tu spyod lam bya ba yang /
NK084(yu)001:3048: rang las ma rtogs pa'i lha sku rtsal du myed de /
NK084(yu)001:3049: rang la ye nas yod pa de nyid spyod lam du byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3051: zhes pa rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de /
NK084(yu)001:3052: shes par byed pa'i dal gyis shes par bya zhes so //
