NK084(yu)001:3054: de ltar rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la ni /
NK084(yu)001:3055: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ste rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3057: zhes rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor las byung ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:3059: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor mchog /zhes pa ting
NK084(yu)001:3060: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dkyil gyi gtso bo
NK084(yu)001:3061: ni mchog gi rdo rje sems dpa' yin pas spyod
NK084(yu)001:3062: lam thams cad du rdo rje sems dpa' bsgom pa'o
NK084(yu)001:3063: // de rnams ni sku bsgom par 'dod pa kho na'o //
NK084(yu)001:3065: ma nyams de'i dbyings su gnas //
NK084(yu)001:3066: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod thams cad du yang stong pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos pas /
NK084(yu)001:3067: de'i ngang la gnas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3068: cung zad blo chung ba 'dra na de'i ngang las rang lha'i skur bskyed nas lus bsrung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:3071: spyod lam thams cad lha'i skur gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK084(yu)001:3072: yang na nang gi rdzogs rims su bshad na /
NK084(yu)001:3074: rang la spyi bo bde' ba chen po'i 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK084(yu)001:3075: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma bcu drug dang /
NK084(yu)001:3076: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma brgyad dang /
NK084(yu)001:3077: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo na rtsa 'dab ma drug cu rtsa bzhir gnas pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3078: srog shing rtsa g.yas ro ma dang /
NK084(yu)001:3080: dbus kun d+har ma dang rnams rang la gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3081: dkyil 'khor gyis ni de ltar gnas pa de shes par gyis so //
NK084(yu)001:3082: dkyil 'khor ni gnas pa de la'o //
NK084(yu)001:3083: bsgom pa ni dkyil 'khor de rnams bsgom pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3084: dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor las byung ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:3085: spyi bo na yi ge ham mgo' thur du lta ba byung bas /
NK084(yu)001:3087: de nas byang sems snying khar byung ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3088: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor mchog ni /
NK084(yu)001:3089: snying ka na rtsa 'dab ma brgyad la /
NK084(yu)001:3093: sems ma brgyad dang rnams gnas par bstan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3094: de bas na gdam ngag tu byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3095: de yis byang chub snying po len //
NK084(yu)001:3097: bla na myed pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras bu chos sku myur du thob bo //
NK084(yu)001:3098: cho ga sngags dang yo byad rnams //
NK084(yu)001:3099: dang po cho ga lnga rdzogs par bsgom ste /
NK084(yu)001:3103: ye shes pa sgrub lnga rdzogs par bya ste /
NK084(yu)001:3104: de nas sngags kyi yan lag lnga ni /
NK084(yu)001:3105: rtsa ba'i lha yab yum dang /
NK084(yu)001:3106: thabs bzhi bcu so sor bsgom kyi lha dang /
NK084(yu)001:3107: shes ye shes sems dpa' rab kyi lha dang /
NK084(yu)001:3108: rdo sku gsung thugsrje gsum gyi lha dang /
NK084(yu)001:3109: bdag dbu' rgyan po'i lha lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:3113: a li ka li yo byad dang lnga'o //
NK084(yu)001:3115: de la dang po cho ga lngas sku gsal bar byed /
NK084(yu)001:3116: de nas sngags kyi yan lag lngas nyi khri bzhi stong la rig pa rtsal sbyang /
NK084(yu)001:3117: de nas yo byad lngas mchod pa dbul lo //
NK084(yu)001:3118: de ltar rig pa rtsal 'byongs nas /
NK084(yu)001:3120: phun sum tshogs lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi'i gzung /
NK084(yu)001:3121: bsnyen sgrub rnam pa bzhi lam gyi gzhung srang /
NK084(yu)001:3122: tshogs lhag gnyis kyis mchod pa'i 'brel ba tha ma 'bras la sbyor ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3123: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK084(yu)001:3124: zhag sum cu phrag drug ni zla ba drug yin te /
NK084(yu)001:3125: dbang po rab kyis zla ba drug na 'grub bo //
NK084(yu)001:3126: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK084(yu)001:3127: dbang po 'bring gis zla ba bcu gnyis sam bcu bzhi na 'grub /
NK084(yu)001:3129: zla ba bcu drug gis 'grub bo //
NK084(yu)001:3130: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK084(yu)001:3131: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob par 'gyur te /
NK084(yu)001:3133: de tshe bcu drug tshun gcad kyis //
NK084(yu)001:3134: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob pa de kho
NK084(yu)001:3135: na'i tshe na phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin yang
NK084(yu)001:3136: / de'i steng du zla ba bcu drug tshun chad bsgrub na /
NK084(yu)001:3137: sgrub pa thob par nges te /
NK084(yu)001:3138: de nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la sbyor ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3139: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK084(yu)001:3140: sku lnga lhun grub rtogs tshul bstan /
NK084(yu)001:3141: de yang yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga lhun grub tu rdzogs pa ni /
NK084(yu)001:3142: rig 'dzin nyid las sgras dpags pa tsam du 'gyur ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3143: sgrib pa dag pa'i ye shes nyid ma rtsal bar
NK084(yu)001:3144: lhun sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las nyi shu
NK084(yu)001:3146: de ni mthar thug pa'i lhun gyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3147: ye shes thig le de nyid las //
NK084(yu)001:3149: ye shes ni lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK084(yu)001:3150: thig le ni sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dbyer myed pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3152: de las khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3153: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK084(yu)001:3154: ye shes thig le de nyid ni /
NK084(yu)001:3155: gzhi' dngos po gnas lugs so //
NK084(yu)001:3156: gnas lugs de ni rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3157: thig le nyid snang ba ni /
NK084(yu)001:3158: rig pas don de nyid rtogs pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3159: bsam gyis myi khyab mtha' yas mchog /de rnams gzhan nas byung ba ma yin te /
NK084(yu)001:3160: gzhi' rang 'byung gi ye shes spros pa thams cad dang bral ba de nyid las /
NK084(yu)001:3161: ye shes kyi rol pa ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3162: ye shes kyi che ba'i yon tan stobs dang mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3163: gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang mtshan dang dpe' byad
NK084(yu)001:3164: thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i yi ge 'khor lo
NK084(yu)001:3165: tshogs chen gyi sa mngon du byas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3166: phyogs bcu dus bzhi mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:3167: lha dang gzhal yas khang bzhugs tshul bstan /
NK084(yu)001:3168: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK084(yu)001:3169: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa de'i bzhugs gnas khyad par can no //
NK084(yu)001:3170: zhing khams gzhal yas rnam dag dang //
NK084(yu)001:3171: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa /
NK084(yu)001:3172: phyi chos kyi dbyings spros pa dang bral ba /
NK084(yu)001:3173: nang 'og min gyi gnas lta bur snang ba /
NK084(yu)001:3174: gsang ba yum gyi mkha' bde stong gi nyams can no //
NK084(yu)001:3175: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK084(yu)001:3176: gzhal yas khang rnam par dag pa rgya yongs su
NK084(yu)001:3177: ma chad pa ni che chung gi tshad dang rgya
NK084(yu)001:3178: dang bral lo // 'khor lo'i rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK084(yu)001:3180: rin po che'i rgyan mang po bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3181: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi lha mo grangs myed pas brgyan pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3182: dkyil 'khor ma lus thams cad kun //
NK084(yu)001:3183: gnas de ni rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK084(yu)001:3184: rgyud yongs su dag pa'i bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs pas /
NK084(yu)001:3185: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad de na gnas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3186: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3187: 'og min gyi gnas kyi dus gsum gyi bde' bar gshegs pa de'i zhal mthong nas /
NK084(yu)001:3188: yid dga' ba dang brod pa khyad par can skyes pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3189: rgya chen gsung las don byung ba //
NK084(yu)001:3190: de lta bu'i sgrib pa shin tu cha phra ba
NK084(yu)001:3191: de bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po'i byin
NK084(yu)001:3192: gyis rlabs las don gyi gsung byung ba yis /
NK084(yu)001:3193: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3195: gsung rang bzhin gyi ye shes ji ltar bar bzod pa thob ste /
NK084(yu)001:3196: ye shes rang snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK084(yu)001:3197: gcig dang du ma bral ba'i //
NK084(yu)001:3198: dngos po rtogs par dka' ba bstan /
NK084(yu)001:3199: gong du bstan pa nyid rang rig par cig pa dang /
NK084(yu)001:3200: rang nyid gcig dang du ma'i mtha' thams cad dang bral zhing grol ba'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:3201: rang rig pa nyid thams cad du ma 'gags par shar bas /
NK084(yu)001:3202: gcig dang du ma'i ma spangs par bral ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3203: mtha' dang dbus myed de bzhin nyid //
NK084(yu)001:3204: de ltar mtha' ma grub pas dbus kyang ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK084(yu)001:3205: mtha' myed dbus myed de bzhin nyid yin no //
NK084(yu)001:3206: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi gzigs te //
NK084(yu)001:3207: de ni bde bar gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi spyan gyis kyang mi gzigs te /
NK084(yu)001:3209: rang 'byung ye shes gnas myed snang //
NK084(yu)001:3210: 'o na myed do mnyam pa la /
NK084(yu)001:3211: rang 'byung ye shes nyid rten gnas myed par snang ba'o //
NK084(yu)001:3212: ci'i phyir na dag pa la rten /
NK084(yu)001:3213: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK084(yu)001:3214: de ltar brtan pa'i 'bras bu de ni /
NK084(yu)001:3215: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa thams cad du mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3216: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK084(yu)001:3217: bde' gshegs yon tan rmad po che //
NK084(yu)001:3218: de ni lam bde' bar gshegs pa /
NK084(yu)001:3219: yon tan gsang ba rmad du byung ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:3220: bde' bar gshegs pa thams cad gcig tu bsdus pa'i ngo bo /
NK084(yu)001:3221: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las kyi bdag po'o //
NK084(yu)001:3222: gzhan na yod pa ma yod pa ma yin te //
NK084(yu)001:3223: de ltar bstan pa'i 'bras bu de dag yang /
NK084(yu)001:3224: gzhan na yod pa snyed pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK084(yu)001:3225: rang rig pa nyid de ltar rang shar bas las ma rtogs pa gzhan myed ces so //
NK084(yu)001:3226: lha srin la sogs smos ci dgos //
NK084(yu)001:3227: de lta bu'i 'bras bu de thob pa ma mi
NK084(yu)001:3228: thob pa ma bden nam mi bden nam mnyam na
NK084(yu)001:3229: / dper na 'jig rten gyi lha bsgrubs pas grub rtags byung na /
NK084(yu)001:3231: 'jig rten lha la yang yon tan yod na /
NK084(yu)001:3232: 'di la lta ci smos zhes pa'o //
NK084(yu)001:3233: rgyud kyi don las sgrub pa'i thabs //
NK084(yu)001:3234: rgyud dpal gsang ba snying po las /
NK084(yu)001:3235: zhi ba'i bsgrub thabs 'di bstus pas so //
NK084(yu)001:3237: rin chen d+r+wa ba 'di bstus pas //
NK084(yu)001:3240: d+r+wa ba ltar thabs shes du 'brel /
NK084(yu)001:3241: rgyud las logs su bkol nas bstus pas /
NK084(yu)001:3242: bcom ldan kun bzang sku gsung thugs //
NK084(yu)001:3243: bcom ldan dpal kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs kyi bcud dngos grub kyi bcud dam pa rnams /
NK084(yu)001:3244: sems can kun gyis thob par shog /bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par shog //
NK084(yu)001:3245: zhi ba rin chen dra ba zhes bya ba //
NK084(yu)001:3246: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa /
NK084(yu)001:3248: //rgya gar gyi pan+di ta sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK084(yu)001:3249: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba bran ka mu ri ta dang /
NK084(yu)001:3250: b+ha man 'dzu sh+ri war mas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab bo //
NK084(yu)001:3251: ston pa ye shes rdo rje'i //
NK084(yu)001:3252: phyag dpe rin chen dra ba las //
NK084(yu)001:3253: shin tu zab pa blo gros yin //
NK084(yu)001:3254: dge ba rang gzhan kun la bsngo //
